Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:55.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1957年10月 蘇聯將\N{\rOriginal text}In October 1957, the Soviet Union launched
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:59.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}世界上第一顆人造衛星 斯普特尼克1號送入軌道\N{\rOriginal text}the world's first artificial satellite, Sputnik 1, into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:04.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這一成就加劇了美蘇兩國之間的太空競賽\N{\rOriginal text}Their achievement fueled a space race between the United States and the Soviets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}之後發生了什麼 人們說法不一\N{\rOriginal text}There has been some debate about what followed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:12.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我親身經歷過 所以接下來講的都是真事 基本上是吧\N{\rOriginal text}but I was there, and this is the real story. Mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}直到兩天前\N{\rOriginal text}Until two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}地球上的人才頭一次聽到這個聲音\N{\rOriginal text}that sound had never been heard on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(蘇聯人將衛星送進太空)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(《生活》 太空競賽)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美國衛星一敗塗地)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美國嘗試發射自己的衛星 結果慘不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:31.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美國火箭計劃啟動失敗)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘇聯成功地將一個人送入太空\N{\rOriginal text}The Soviet Union has sent a man into space
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(第一個進入太空的人)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}並把他活著帶回地球\N{\rOriginal text}and brought him back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘇聯人在全世界範圍內\N{\rOriginal text}The Soviets made the most of the flight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:41.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大肆宣傳這次航天行動 其國內自然也是舉國歡慶\N{\rOriginal text}in their worldwide propaganda. Naturally, there was jubilation in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在認識到蘇聯人取得領先後\N{\rOriginal text}Recognizing the head start obtained by the Soviets,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:51.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我認為我國應致力於實現一個目標\N{\rOriginal text}I believe that this nation should commit itself to achieving the goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}即在這個十年內\N{\rOriginal text}before this decade is out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:57.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}把一個人送上月球並讓他安全返回地球\N{\rOriginal text}of landing a man on the moon and returning him safely to the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美國宇航員環繞地球飛行)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們選擇在這個十年登月\N{\rOriginal text}We choose to go to the moon in this decade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}並完成其他壯舉 不是因為這個目標輕而易舉\N{\rOriginal text}and do the other things, not because they are easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而是因為它困難重重\N{\rOriginal text}but because they are hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為這個挑戰是我們願意接受\N{\rOriginal text}Because that challenge is one that we are willing to accept,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不願推遲 並準備大獲全勝的\N{\rOriginal text}one we are unwilling to postpone, and one we intend to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}指揮飛行員 一 二 三 四 五\N{\rOriginal text}Command Pilot. One, two, three, four, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}五 四 三 二 一\N{\rOriginal text}Five, four, three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}著火了\N{\rOriginal text}Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}駕駛艙裏失火了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got a fire in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快出去 我們要燒死了\N{\rOriginal text}Let's get out! We're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:42.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}宇航員維吉爾·格裏森 愛德華·懷特 和羅傑·查菲不幸遇難\N{\rOriginal text}Astronauts Virgil Grissom, Edward White and Roger Chaffee have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}媒體官員稱 因為此次悲劇事件\N{\rOriginal text}Press officials say because of the tragedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅1號飛行任務將被無限期推遲\N{\rOriginal text}the Apollo 1 flight has now been postponed indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 登月之旅很有吸引力\N{\rOriginal text}I... It's, uh... It's a groovy trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:53.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但在美國 還有很多更重要的事情要先做\N{\rOriginal text}but there are a lot more important things to do first in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也許把這些事情都搞定了 我們才能登月\N{\rOriginal text}Maybe when all that's taken care of we can afford to go to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:59.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們發現自己物質豐富 士氣低下\N{\rOriginal text}We find ourselves rich in goods but ragged in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}雄心勃勃地想要登月\N{\rOriginal text}Reaching with magnificent precision for the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}卻在地球上陷入一片混亂\N{\rOriginal text}but falling into raucous discord on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們想要和平 卻被捲入戰爭\N{\rOriginal text}We are caught at war wanting peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們想要團結 卻四分五裂\N{\rOriginal text}We're torn by division wanting unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這個巨大的土星號火箭\N{\rOriginal text}This giant Saturn rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}以及這裏的其他設備 最初都是這場競賽的一部分\N{\rOriginal text}and the rest of the equipment here began as part of a race
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(國家航空航天局預算削減)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}為的是戰勝蘇聯人 它們肩負著\N{\rOriginal text}to beat the Russians with the national goal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我國在這個十年內把人類送上月球的目標\N{\rOriginal text}of putting a man on the moon in this decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但登月之旅的花費將超出所有人的預期\N{\rOriginal text}But their trip will cost more than anyone thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:28.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而在1960年代成功登月的幾率愈加渺茫\N{\rOriginal text}And their chances of landing on the moon in the 1960s are increasingly slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(國家航空航天局)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}斯圖 你當主管第一周 聽著情況不妙啊\N{\rOriginal text}First week as manager, Stu. Doesn't sound like it's going great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要麼是計量表不准 要麼是某個儲存罐漏了\N{\rOriginal text}So either our meters are off or there's a breach in one of the tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但這種情況沒有規程 我們也找不到洩漏源頭\N{\rOriginal text}But there's no protocol for this. And we can't source the leak
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為是液態... 液態氫\N{\rOriginal text}because it's liquid hyd... Liquid hydrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它是無色無味的 所有人都出去 快\N{\rOriginal text}It's colorless and odorless. Everybody out! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}裏德 凱爾 放下鉛筆\N{\rOriginal text}Reed, Kyle, pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可能已經在燃燒了 我們卻不知情 找門出去\N{\rOriginal text}It could be burning, and we wouldn't know it. Find a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快 跑起來 別慢吞吞的\N{\rOriginal text}Come on! Run, run! No walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他在幹什麼? 打掃嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}What's he doing? Is he cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 這是... 一種檢查洩漏的老辦法\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. It's an... It's an old-school leak detection process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他用的是把掃帚\N{\rOriginal text}It's a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}斯圖 你很聰明的 再想想 干麥稈加上液態氫等於...\N{\rOriginal text}Stu, you're better than this. Come on. Straw plus liquid hydrogen equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 沒事了 別擔心了 來吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right, we're good! Don't worry about it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們還有工作呢 快點\N{\rOriginal text}We got work to do. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}新的規程是用掃帚檢查洩漏\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, the new protocol is the broom method.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們需要一把新掃帚\N{\rOriginal text}We need a new broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我剛才真以為他死了\N{\rOriginal text}I for sure thought he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜託\N{\rOriginal text}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這還是\N{\rOriginal text}It's still broke
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你上次發脾氣時弄壞的 是的 我能看出來\N{\rOriginal text}from the last time you were in a mood. Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}波音又來電話了 亨利 打給議會 別找我\N{\rOriginal text}Boeing called again. Call Congress, Henry, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我沒有他們的電話號碼\N{\rOriginal text}I don't have their number.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每天... 這裏都有東西壞掉\N{\rOriginal text}Every day, every day, something is breaking around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:24.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}或者爆炸 我們資金不足 人手不足\N{\rOriginal text}Or blowing up. We're underfunded, under... understaffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但沒錯 他們還期望我們吊打蘇聯人\N{\rOriginal text}But yeah, we're still expected to beat the pants off the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你能告訴我到底該怎麼做到嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You mind telling me how the hell we're supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就從善待自動售貨機開始吧\N{\rOriginal text}Could start by being a little nicer to the vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快看 在那裏\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什麼? 有一隻貓\N{\rOriginal text}What? There's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那又怎麼了? 是一隻黑貓 亨利 代表霉運\N{\rOriginal text}So what? It's a black cat, Henry. It's bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 不見了\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 謝天謝地 好吧 我們走\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Thank God. Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}叫保安 不要\N{\rOriginal text}Call security. I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不叫 這... 你要去叫\N{\rOriginal text}I will not. It... Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們這裏最不該出現的就是一隻黑貓\N{\rOriginal text}The last thing that we need around here is a black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}保安又不管這種事\N{\rOriginal text}They don't deal with things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們管的 現在管了\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, they do. They do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你反應過頭了 不 是你反應遲鈍\N{\rOriginal text}Y-You're overreacting. No, you're not overreacting enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}立刻叫保安 馬上去\N{\rOriginal text}Call 'em right now. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我看起來如何?\N{\rOriginal text}How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}容光煥發 加油\N{\rOriginal text}You're glowing. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下午好 小伙子們\N{\rOriginal text}Good afternoon, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}走錯房間了 親愛的 我們不需要筆錄\N{\rOriginal text}Wrong room, sweetheart. We don't need dictation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:28.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我叫凱莉·瓊斯 今天的會議由我主持\N{\rOriginal text}I'm Kelly Jones. I'll be running the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們一定是菲爾·亨利 尼爾·布朗和...\N{\rOriginal text}You must be Phil Hunley, Neil Brown and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:34.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}扎克·坦納 不介意我坐下吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh. [chuckles] Zack Tanner. You don't mind if I sit down, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}恕我直言 瓊斯太太 我們是一家進步的公司\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, all due respect, Mrs. Jones, we're a progressive company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們的速記員團隊有16名女性\N{\rOriginal text}We employ 16 women in our steno pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:44.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們向男人出售跑車 出售300馬力...\N{\rOriginal text}We're selling sports cars to men. We're selling a 300 horsepower...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:48.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}355馬力 你們賣的是7014CC排量 V8引擎的猛獸\N{\rOriginal text}355, 428 cubic inch V-8 beast is what you're selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們要著重推銷車的速度 比如這個\N{\rOriginal text}You want to focus on the car's speed. Something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:58.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}眼熟嗎? 雪佛蘭科邁羅 龐蒂亞克火鳥 還有奧斯莫比爾\N{\rOriginal text}Look familiar? Chevy Camaro. Pontiac Firebird. And Oldsmobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}都是上個月的\N{\rOriginal text}All from last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幸好你們有些競爭對手沒有的東西\N{\rOriginal text}Thankfully, you have something that your competition doesn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:09.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}野馬Fastback 「給他355馬力 給家人安全帶」\N{\rOriginal text}The Mustang Fastback. "355 horses for him. Seat belts for the family."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:13.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}安全帶? 我們安裝安全帶 只是因為明年可能會有強制安裝的規定\N{\rOriginal text}The seat belts? We only put them in because they might be mandatory next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們來做個遊戲吧\N{\rOriginal text}Let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我來猜你們幾位先生分別駕駛什麼車\N{\rOriginal text}Now I'm gonna guess what kind of car each one of you gentlemen drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:28.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}扎克 1966年款福特野馬敞篷車 罌粟紅色的\N{\rOriginal text}Zack, Ford Mustang '66 convertible. It's poppy red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:35.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不過你們當了老公的人不會開野馬 尼爾開林肯大陸\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, no Mustangs for you husbands though. A Lincoln Continental for Neil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:43.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可憐的菲爾開客貨兩用車 菲爾 你知道我每天什麼時候最開心嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}A station wagon for poor Phil. Oh, Phil. You know what the best part of my day is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是我老公查理晚上回家時\N{\rOriginal text}When my husband Charlie comes home at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:55.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我無法想像他有一天晚上不回家會怎樣\N{\rOriginal text}I can't even imagine what it would be like if-if one night he... he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你來想像一下這段對話\N{\rOriginal text}Now imagine the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果有人跟你老婆說這輛車\N{\rOriginal text}if someone told your wife that this car,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}擁有355馬力和169公里的最高時速\N{\rOriginal text}its 355 horses and 105 top speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:10.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}正是這輛車每天晚上 載著她老公安全回到家人身邊\N{\rOriginal text}this car is what brings her husband home safe to her family every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她希望你擁有這輛車\N{\rOriginal text}Now she wants you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她說出每個已婚男士夢想聽到的話\N{\rOriginal text}She says the words every married man dreams of hearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「如果你買下這輛野馬\N{\rOriginal text}"I'd feel so much better
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我會感覺比現在更幸福 親愛的」\N{\rOriginal text}if you bought yourself that Mustang, sweetheart."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎麼猜到他們開什麼車的?\N{\rOriginal text}How did you guess what kind of cars they drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}賄賂了他們的秘書還是怎樣?\N{\rOriginal text}What, bribe their secretaries or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉 真的假的\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兩包維珍妮牌女士香煙和一瓶帕科香水\N{\rOriginal text}Two packs of Virginia Slims and a bottle of Paco Rabanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每個人都是有價的\N{\rOriginal text}Everyone has their price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幸好剛才我的羊水沒破 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}I'm just lucky that my water didn't break in there. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 羅恩 你老婆好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Hi, Ron. How's the wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(創意總監 凱莉·瓊斯)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 假肚子只能乾洗\N{\rOriginal text}Now, the baby bump, dry-clean only.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 我記下了 還有 歐米茄確認了下周的安排\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, I have that noted. A-Also, Omega confirmed for next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我完成了芭斯·羅繽的畫\N{\rOriginal text}I finished the Baskin-Robbins artwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}Palmex那個人問你的地址 想給你送玫瑰\N{\rOriginal text}and that guy from Palmex asked for your address to send roses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我給了他我的 我知道\N{\rOriginal text}but I gave him mine because I know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你對玫瑰的看法 你知道我對玫瑰的看法\N{\rOriginal text}how you feel about roses. You know how I feel about roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:08.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還有 約翰又來電了 他想在星期二帶你去吃晚餐\N{\rOriginal text}Also, John called. Again. He wants to take you to dinner Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}告訴他我搬到洛杉磯去了 給陶氏化學的布魯斯打電話\N{\rOriginal text}Tell him I moved to LA. And call Bruce from Dow Chemical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我聽說他們在給密保諾密封袋找新代理\N{\rOriginal text}I hear they're looking for a new agency for Ziploc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人們應該抵制陶氏化學 他們做凝固汽油彈\N{\rOriginal text}People should be boycotting Dow. They make napalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人們嘴上說著抵制 但還是在買裝三文治的袋子\N{\rOriginal text}People say they're boycotting, but they're still buying sandwich bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們還賣保鮮膜和泡沫塑料\N{\rOriginal text}They also sell Saran Wrap and Styrofoam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你認為人們會停止使用泡沫塑料嗎? 你的咖啡用什麼裝的?\N{\rOriginal text}Think people are going to stop using Styrofoam? What's your coffee in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 我知道你和你的朋友們想拯救世界\N{\rOriginal text}Now, I know you and your friends want to save the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但等到你在1984年當上這裏的主管\N{\rOriginal text}and by the time you're running this place in 1984,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}世上已經沒有核彈 全體人類平權了\N{\rOriginal text}there's gonna be no nukes and equal rights for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但在那之前 我們得幹好本職工作\N{\rOriginal text}But until then, we've got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:39.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉... 我們有大麻煩了\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly! Kelly! Kelly. Kelly. We've got a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:43.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我剛剛憤怒地離開片場 對 我有充分的理由\N{\rOriginal text}I just stormed off set, and, yes, it was justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我沒法跟胡佛這些人合作\N{\rOriginal text}I cannot work with these Hoover people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:50.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}顯然他們對我給他們拍廣告的方式有意見\N{\rOriginal text}Apparently, they have issues with the way that I am shooting their commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們真是這麼說的 「他們的」 那可是我的廣告\N{\rOriginal text}They actually said that. "Their." It's my commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不就是做吸塵器的嘛 我可是搞藝術的\N{\rOriginal text}They make vacuums. I make art.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 我們約了見面嗎? 沒有...\N{\rOriginal text}Sorry, did we have a meeting set? No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不好意思 我沒意識到還得約時間\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. I didn't realize I had to set a time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}才能跟最親愛的朋友說話\N{\rOriginal text}to speak to one of my dearest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上次我們說話時你把我炒了 我現在不為你工作了\N{\rOriginal text}The last time we spoke, you fired me. And I don't work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟你講 凱莉 我不是來聽你訓斥的\N{\rOriginal text}You know what, Kelly, I didn't come in here to be berated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是來找你支持我的\N{\rOriginal text}I came in to be agreed with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:09.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你十分鐘後要向雀巢推銷 這很重要\N{\rOriginal text}You have that Nestle pitch in ten. Very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}騙人的 再見\N{\rOriginal text}That is a lie. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:15.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘭斯 給你拿到這份導演工作 堪稱聖誕奇跡\N{\rOriginal text}Lance, getting you this directing gig was a Christmas miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你搞砸了那個果凍廣告拍攝後 我用了三周時間\N{\rOriginal text}It took me three weeks to convince them that you were stable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}才說服他們你並非喜怒無常 果凍廣告那事不怪我\N{\rOriginal text}after your Jell-O shoot from hell. Jell-O was not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那個演員... 才五歲 你把他弄哭了\N{\rOriginal text}Ugh. That actor wa... Was five. You made him cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是幫了那孩子一把 好萊塢可不好混\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I did that child a favor. Hollywood is no cakewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那亨氏食品廣告呢? 你超了預算四萬塊 只是個番茄醬廣告而已\N{\rOriginal text}What about the Heinz commercial? You went 40,000 over budget. It was about ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:34.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}才不是 重點是番茄醬帶來的希望\N{\rOriginal text}It was not about ketchup. It was about the promise of ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有人看到我在為他們的產品做什麼\N{\rOriginal text}No one sees what I'm doing for their products.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我在提升產品價值\N{\rOriginal text}I am elevating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我現在應該在拍電影了\N{\rOriginal text}I should be in film by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我拒絕了執導《娃娃谷》的機會\N{\rOriginal text}I passed on directing Valley of the Dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那事怪我 但我還是該拍電影 好了 我們是怎麼稱呼你的?\N{\rOriginal text}That is on me, but still. Now, what do we call you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}廣告界的庫布裏克 好了 天啊 斯坦利是半吊子\N{\rOriginal text}The Kubrick of commercials. All right. Oh, my God. Stanley is a hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拍出一部好電影就突然成了天才\N{\rOriginal text}He does one good movie, and suddenly he's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是傳奇 好嗎? 創意天才\N{\rOriginal text}You are a legend, right? Creative genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你也脾氣暴躁 反覆無常 永遠不能按預算拍攝\N{\rOriginal text}You're also hotheaded, mercurial and can't stick to a budget for shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝 這不是誇你\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, thank you. That wasn't a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這時就該當耳旁風 你若不跟胡佛合作 以後就沒人請你了\N{\rOriginal text}It is when you stop listening. If you quit Hoover, you'll be unhirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘭斯 不如你回片場吧\N{\rOriginal text}Lance, why don't you march your ass back to set,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不管發什麼脾氣 都道個歉 好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}and you apologize for whatever fit you threw, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}給你男朋友買個棒棒的聖誕禮物 謝謝他容忍你\N{\rOriginal text}Buy your boyfriend something nice for Christmas for putting up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也給我買個禮物 好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Get something for me too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:17.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聖誕快樂 蘭斯 聖誕快樂\N{\rOriginal text}Merry Christmas, Lance. Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請你給我找份像樣的工作 好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you get me a decent job, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅8號於今早成功發射\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 8 launched successfully this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:32.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這場勝利是國家航空航天局的及時雨 在越南方面 今天有更多人犧牲\N{\rOriginal text}A much needed win for NASA. In Vietnam, more men were lost today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:32.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波羅8號發射錄影)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}二千五百萬公里...\N{\rOriginal text}And 15 million miles...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}麻煩再來一杯 另外把晚餐菜單拿給我\N{\rOriginal text}I'll have another round, please, and a look at the dinner menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 女士 謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, ma'am. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今晚有兩個特色菜 雞肉餡餅和洛克菲勒牡蠣\N{\rOriginal text}Two specials tonight. Chicken potpie and Oysters Rockefeller.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們吃雞好了 她對牡蠣過敏\N{\rOriginal text}We'll do the chicken. She's allergic to oysters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:53.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}給我來一杯麥卡倫 一個檸檬和一個砧板\N{\rOriginal text}And I'll take a shot of Macallan, a lemon and a cutting board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 先生 不好意思 我認識你嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, sir. Oh, I'm sorry. Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:01.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跑車上裝安全帶 這個點子很不錯\N{\rOriginal text}Seat belts in a sports car. I mean, that's a great angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很不幸 他們即將停止跟你合作\N{\rOriginal text}Unfortunately, they're about to kill the account.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}為什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:11.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為有人告訴他們 你肚子裏其實沒孩子\N{\rOriginal text}Because someone told them that you don't really have a bun in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}菲爾 讓我解釋一下\N{\rOriginal text}Phil. [chuckles] Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我以後再也不會相信女人了\N{\rOriginal text}That's the last time I trust a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我還給你送了一份嬰兒禮物\N{\rOriginal text}I actually sent you a baby gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你那麼做非常貼心 請讓我...\N{\rOriginal text}Which was so sweet, by the way. Let me just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾 讓我解釋一下 如果你們...\N{\rOriginal text}Neil, let-let me explain. If you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼回事? 你為誰工作? 奧美廣告?\N{\rOriginal text}What is this? Who do you work for, Ogilvy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你業績拼不過我 就害我被解雇?\N{\rOriginal text}Huh? You can't outsell me, so you got me fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}恰恰相反 我想聘請你\N{\rOriginal text}Just the opposite. I wanna hire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我叫莫·伯克斯 在總統辦公室工作\N{\rOriginal text}Name's Moe Berkus. I work for the president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哪家公司的?\N{\rOriginal text}Of what company?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美國總統\N{\rOriginal text}The president.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:54.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們需要一位營銷專家 聽說你是最厲害的\N{\rOriginal text}We need a, uh, marketing specialist, and word has it you are the very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:13:00.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}於是我做了些調研 發現...\N{\rOriginal text}So I did a little digging, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的經歷很有趣 凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}You have quite a colorful past, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還是說我該叫你簡? 來自芝加哥的空姐\N{\rOriginal text}Or should I call you Jane? Stewardess from Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:11.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也許你更喜歡被稱為艾米 俄亥俄州的護士\N{\rOriginal text}Or perhaps you would prefer Amy, the nurse from Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有這麼漂亮的臉蛋 誰還會看推薦信?\N{\rOriginal text}Face like that, who's gonna check references?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你找的那一頁不在這裏\N{\rOriginal text}Page you're looking for isn't in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不知道你在說什麼\N{\rOriginal text}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你當然不知道 我懂\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, sure you don't. And I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:32.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 我也有幾十個身份證 我的真名也不叫莫\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, I have dozens of IDs, and my real name's not Moe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有那麼多名字可以選 你卻挑了「莫」?\N{\rOriginal text}With all the names you could've picked, you landed on Moe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你天賦出眾\N{\rOriginal text}You have singular talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:41.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可以用來成就更偉大的事業 何必浪費在賣車上呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Why waste it selling cars when you can think bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫 有什麼公司比福特更偉大?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, Moe, what's bigger than Ford?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你去過佛羅里達州嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You ever been to Florida?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們想讓你推銷月球? 月球 阿波羅任務\N{\rOriginal text}They want you to sell the moon? The moon. The Apollo mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一整套\N{\rOriginal text}The whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這個叫莫的傢伙為國家航空航天局做事?\N{\rOriginal text}And this Moe guy works for NASA?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:08.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 不 算是吧 他是政府的人\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. I mean, y... Well, no. Um, kind of. He-He-He works for the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哪個部門?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:19.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這個人... 我們在為理查德·尼克松工作?\N{\rOriginal text}Does this guy... Are we working for Richard Nixon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為我才不會為理查德·尼克松工作 凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Because, Kelly, I will not work for Richard Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是持證女權主義者 我真的有證\N{\rOriginal text}I'm a card-carrying feminist. I actually have a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我甚至不相信他要當總統了\N{\rOriginal text}I can't even believe he's going to be president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我本來不知道自己對美國有這麼多意見\N{\rOriginal text}I had no idea I disagreed with this much of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:33.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們為國家航空航天局工作 推銷月球 沒人對月球有意見\N{\rOriginal text}We are working for NASA to sell the moon. Nobody disagrees about the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是 你我都清楚\N{\rOriginal text}No. You and I both know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們身邊每天都有可怕的事發生\N{\rOriginal text}that everywhere around us every day something terrible is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}無所不在\N{\rOriginal text}Everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除了太空\N{\rOriginal text}Except in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真討厭 你說動我了 他們絕對需要我們的幫助\N{\rOriginal text}I hate that this is working on me. They definitely need our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:48.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道國家航空航天局的頭29次任務 只有48%的成功率嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Did you know of NASA's first 29 missions, only 48% have been successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這不可能 太離譜了\N{\rOriginal text}That can't be. That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:56.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道可可海灘市的 男女比例是五比一嗎? 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}Did you know the ratio of men to women in Cocoa Beach is 5-to-1? [chuckles] Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}只要你給我們找的住處不在兄弟會街就行\N{\rOriginal text}As long as you got us a quiet place that's not on Frat Row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}指南手冊說那裏很古雅\N{\rOriginal text}The... The guidebook said it's quaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(衛星汽車旅館 客滿)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你被炒魷魚了\N{\rOriginal text}You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這些都是什麼人啊?\N{\rOriginal text}Who are all these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今天星期三 他們好像在另一個星球上\N{\rOriginal text}It is a Wednesday. It's like they're on a different planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏叫佛羅里達\N{\rOriginal text}They call it Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請告訴我你訂了一個遠離游泳池的房間\N{\rOriginal text}Please tell me you booked a room away from the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}16 21 天氣\N{\rOriginal text}sixteen and 21... Weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}明天晴間多雲\N{\rOriginal text}Clear to partly cloudy tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下午及傍晚 局部地區有雷陣雨\N{\rOriginal text}A few isolated thundershowers during the afternoon and early evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(佛羅里達州 可可海灘)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今晚最低氣溫18至24攝氏度\N{\rOriginal text}A low tonight, 65 to 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}目前月球火箭發射場周邊城市 氣溫25攝氏度\N{\rOriginal text}Currently 77 in the Moonport cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:51.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏是KO2020電台 為你帶來的體育新聞和天氣預報\N{\rOriginal text}That's KO twenty-twenty news, sports and weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}WKKO\N{\rOriginal text}WKKO...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:55.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(沃爾菲餐廳)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 喬 晚上好 科爾 來點什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, Joe. Evening, Cole. What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}黑咖啡\N{\rOriginal text}Coffee. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:09.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}再來點最快能打包帶走的吃的 朋友\N{\rOriginal text}And whatever takes the least amount of time to put in a bag, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}小姐 你很惹火\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, miss, you're on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真有創意\N{\rOriginal text}Very original.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}得了 我不想跟你玩乾柴烈火\N{\rOriginal text}No, I do not wanna stop, drop and roll with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是 你的書著火了\N{\rOriginal text}No, your book is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊\N{\rOriginal text}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:58.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 沒事的... 我的天\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. All right. All right. All right. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 謝謝你 我只是... 教你個經驗法則\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. Thank you. I just... Just as a rule of thumb,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}酒精和火焰 絕配\N{\rOriginal text}alcohol and flames, they... they like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 天啊 我把你的外套燒壞了\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Oh, gosh. I-I-I ruined your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒事 這衣服跟我出生入死\N{\rOriginal text}No, this thing's seen worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}經歷過千錘百煉 請你喝一杯補償你吧\N{\rOriginal text}Been through worse. Let me buy a drink for your troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不必了 必須的\N{\rOriginal text}That's not necessary. I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不喝酒 沒關係\N{\rOriginal text}I don't drink. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真的? 不喝酒的宇航員 真有意思\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, really? An astronaut who doesn't drink. That's very intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎麼會認為我是宇航員?\N{\rOriginal text}What makes you think I'm an astronaut?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為你戴著阿波羅胸針 只有宇航員才有\N{\rOriginal text}Because you have an Apollo pin, and only astronauts get those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看來你對國家航空航天局略知一二\N{\rOriginal text}So you know a thing or two about NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:27.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 我是新晉粉絲 我叫凱莉·瓊斯\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, well, I'm a recent fan. I'm Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:31.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不是宇航員 我只是在肯尼迪中心工作 科爾·戴維斯\N{\rOriginal text}I'm no astronaut. I just work at Kennedy. Cole Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你做什麼工作?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, what do you do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:39.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 我最不願意在閒聊中談工作\N{\rOriginal text}Uh... Look, the last thing I want to do is make small talk about my job. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 我不是那個意思\N{\rOriginal text}Sorry. That didn't sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不是想... 沒關係 對 你只是實話實說\N{\rOriginal text}I didn't mean it for it to... Uh. That's okay. No. You were being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你點的餐好了 科爾\N{\rOriginal text}Order up, Cole. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我沒實話實說 如果我真的坦誠\N{\rOriginal text}I wasn't being honest. If I was being honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我會跟你說 你是我記憶中\N{\rOriginal text}I'd have told you you're the most beautiful woman
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所見過最美的女人\N{\rOriginal text}that I've seen in longer than I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而我的記憶力很好\N{\rOriginal text}and I have a very good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只想請你喝一杯 然後跟你聊上幾小時\N{\rOriginal text}All I really want to do is just buy you a drink and talk to you for hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我做不到 所以我要努力忘記你在這裏\N{\rOriginal text}but I can't so I'm trying really hard to just forget that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很高興認識你 凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}It was nice to meet you, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常抱歉\N{\rOriginal text}I really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}歡迎來到火箭路\N{\rOriginal text}Welcome to Rockets Road,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:30.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}又稱鱷魚巷\N{\rOriginal text}also known as Alligator Alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果想保住胳膊和腿\N{\rOriginal text}You'll wanna keep your arms and legs inside the cart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請不要把手腳伸出車外\N{\rOriginal text}if you wanna keep your arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有啦 開個小玩笑 它們主要在水中發動攻擊\N{\rOriginal text}No, that's just a little joke. They mostly attack in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(國家航空航天局 約翰F 肯尼迪航天中心)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:46.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 今天的參觀大約要兩個半到三小時\N{\rOriginal text}Now, today's tour will take approximately two and a half to three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請舒適地坐好\N{\rOriginal text}So let's get comfy-cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}右手邊是我們的測試樓\N{\rOriginal text}Now on the right is our testing facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是世界頂尖水平的\N{\rOriginal text}State-of-the-art.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}失火了 它經常失火\N{\rOriginal text}It's on fire. It is often on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:01.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}前方是載具組裝大樓\N{\rOriginal text}Up ahead, we have the vehicle assembly building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:04.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是組裝火箭的地方\N{\rOriginal text}That's where they assemble the rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:10.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是全世界最高的單層建築\N{\rOriginal text}That is the tallest single-story building in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}裏面能放下四座自由女神像\N{\rOriginal text}You can fit four Statue of Liberties inside that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 《生活》雜誌 完全沒拍出它有多壯觀\N{\rOriginal text}Wow. Life Magazine really doesn't do it justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這也太... 我想進去看看\N{\rOriginal text}This is so gre... I'd love to go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏嚴禁入內 抱歉 走 我們靠近點看看\N{\rOriginal text}It's highly restricted. I'm sorry. Come on, let's get a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行... 這裏不得進入\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, no, no. No. There's no entry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你需要一個特殊的胸卡才能進\N{\rOriginal text}You need a special access badge to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}比如這個? 對\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, like... like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那... 不行... 那是我的胸卡\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. That's, uh... Oh, no, no, no, that's... that's my badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 看看這地方 太大了\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, hey... Oh. Look at this place. It's enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}似乎大得多... 她們拿走了我的胸卡\N{\rOriginal text}It seems like it's much bigger... They took my badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看看這個建築\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, look at this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}喂 那是我的胸卡 你好 先生 嗨\N{\rOriginal text}Hello? That's-That's my badge. Hello, sir. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是國家航空航天局 公共事務部的凱莉·瓊斯\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly Jones from NASA Public Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是我們倆的萬能通行證 謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}Here's our all-access pass for both of us. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝 等等... 我的胸卡\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you. Wait, wait. My card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這個我能推銷出去\N{\rOriginal text}Now, this I can sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:01.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}喲呼\N{\rOriginal text}Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們好 小伙子們...\N{\rOriginal text}Hello. Boys, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 凱莉·瓊斯\N{\rOriginal text}Hi. Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:09.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是國家航空航天局 新成立的公共事務部的\N{\rOriginal text}I'm from the new NASA Public Affairs team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我能問你們倆幾個問題嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Can I ask you two a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}姓名 年齡 你們在這裏的工作?\N{\rOriginal text}Name, age, and what's your job here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:19.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是斯圖·布萊斯 總工程師之一 24歲\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, I'm Stu Bryce. One of the, uh, head engineers, and I'm 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們就說35歲 好\N{\rOriginal text}We'll say 35. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你呢?\N{\rOriginal text}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:24.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我叫唐·哈珀 我是他的手下 23歲\N{\rOriginal text}I'm Don Harper. I-I work for him, and I'm 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們真年輕\N{\rOriginal text}You guys are babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}國家航空航天局的平均年齡是26歲\N{\rOriginal text}The average age at NASA is 26.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我們知道這裏也有些老年人\N{\rOriginal text}But w-we do know some old people that work here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 32 33歲的 是\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, like, 32, 33. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽你們這麼說 我很想殺了你倆\N{\rOriginal text}I'll try not to kill both of you for saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:39.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟我們說說 斯圖 你為什麼加入這偉大的美國任務?\N{\rOriginal text}So, tell us, Stu, what brings you to join this great American mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我在大學宿舍里看到了一張傳單\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I s... saw a, uh, flyer in my college dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「從小就熱愛群星」 很好\N{\rOriginal text}"A childhood love of the stars." That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常感人 非常好\N{\rOriginal text}That's very moving. That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你呢? 不好意思\N{\rOriginal text}And you? Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎麼來了?\N{\rOriginal text}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:56.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我特意來找你的 想給你我的電話號碼\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I... I tracked you down to give you my phone number,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為我感覺我們很來電\N{\rOriginal text}'cause I felt we had a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什麼? 別緊張 我開玩笑的\N{\rOriginal text}What? Relax. I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我現在在這裏工作 莫·伯克斯招我進來 改組國家航空航天局公共事務部\N{\rOriginal text}I work here now. Moe Berkus brought me on to revamp NASA Public Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:07.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你就是來自曼哈頓的廣告精英\N{\rOriginal text}So you're the killer from Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你一定就是發射主管 這是我的同事露比·馬丁\N{\rOriginal text}And you must be the launch director. This is my associate, Ruby Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我不在乎 聽著 這棟樓完全禁止進入\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, I don't care. Look. This building is completely off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏有各種可能燒傷 凍傷 烤焦\N{\rOriginal text}Everything in here can burn you, freeze you, fry you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:18.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}毒死 砸死你們的東西\N{\rOriginal text}poison you and crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}走吧 出去 你在這裏工作多久了?\N{\rOriginal text}So let's go. Out. How long have you worked here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:23.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很長時間了\N{\rOriginal text}A substantial amount of time. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:25.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你在寫什麼? 你的原話\N{\rOriginal text}What are you writing? Your quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:27.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這不算原話 我只是隨口一說\N{\rOriginal text}That's not a quote. It was just a thing that I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我會添油加醋的 你今天有時間接受採訪嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}I'll punch it up. Do you have time today for an interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我還需要跟你的上級談談\N{\rOriginal text}And also, I need to sit down with your senior officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上相的優先 我可以幫忙挑\N{\rOriginal text}The photogenic types first. I can help with the selection process.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 我這裏的人都太奇怪了 不適合採訪\N{\rOriginal text}Look, my guys are too weird for interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:38.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而且他們真的在忙生死攸關的工作\N{\rOriginal text}and they're actually busy doing life-and-death work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:42.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 我不需要你的批准\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you know, I don't need your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:45.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美國人跟太空之間 漫長且昂貴的蜜月期已經結束\N{\rOriginal text}The Americans are over their long and expensive honeymoon in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是來提醒大家當初為什麼愛上太空的\N{\rOriginal text}and I'm here to remind them why they fell in love in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:51.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是嗎? 美國人應該心存感激\N{\rOriginal text}Is that right? Well, Americans should be very grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這些人為了這項任務在冒生命危險\N{\rOriginal text}that these men are putting their lives on the line for the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:58.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你並不怎麼瞭解美國人 是吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you don't know much about American people, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:02.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你也不怎麼瞭解 你的辦公室吧? 我帶你看看\N{\rOriginal text}You don't know very much about your office I'm about to show you, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:11.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是儲物間嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Is this a storage closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:13.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是 儲物間有窗戶\N{\rOriginal text}Nope. Storage closet has a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:16.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 速溶咖啡在休息室\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, so, instant coffee... is in the break room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}記得先把水龍頭打開 放一分鐘的水 把鐵銹沖掉\N{\rOriginal text}Just run the tap for a minute to flush out the rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們有誰會用滅火器嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Do either of you know how to work a fire extinguisher?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:27.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不會? 好吧 四步口訣 很簡單\N{\rOriginal text}No? Mkay. PASS method's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拔安全銷 對準火焰 壓下把手 噴向火焰\N{\rOriginal text}Just, uh, pull the pin, aim, squeeze, sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果你們有任何其他需要\N{\rOriginal text}If you need anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:36.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可以回紐約去拿 祝你們愉快\N{\rOriginal text}uh, maybe just go back to New York and get it. Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:41.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}至少他還算養眼 但說話很刺耳\N{\rOriginal text}Well, at least he's easy on the eyes. He's hard on the ears though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:44.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}歡迎儀式很爛啊 我以為你說他們想要我們幫忙呢\N{\rOriginal text}Not a great welcome wagon. I thought you said they wanted our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:47.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我說他們需要我們幫忙 這一點現在已經實錘到不能再實錘\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, no. I said they needed our help. And I do believe that now more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:50.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果我們誰都不能談或什麼都不能看\N{\rOriginal text}How are we supposed to do that if we can't talk to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:52.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那要怎麼幫忙?\N{\rOriginal text}or look at anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:55.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是一隻貓...\N{\rOriginal text}Aw, it's a cat. It's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:56.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是一隻貓 是一隻貓\N{\rOriginal text}It's a cat! It's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:58.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道關於黑貓的說法嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You know what they say about black cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:01.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果黑貓從你面前路過 可能是要去其他地方\N{\rOriginal text}If they cross your path, they're probably going someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:05.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 該把舊名片夾翻出來了\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, time to dig out the old Rolodex.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:08.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}創意時間到\N{\rOriginal text}Let's get creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.61,0:24:34.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅11號將把我們的人送上月球\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11 will land our men on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.49,0:24:37.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這會讓我們成為世界第一\N{\rOriginal text}and that makes us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:40.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果我們完成工作 將會在那裏發射\N{\rOriginal text}If we do our jobs, we will launch right from there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:43.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}時間是7月16日一大早\N{\rOriginal text}July 16, bright and early.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:44.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在那之前\N{\rOriginal text}Between now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:47.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們要完成人類歷史上\N{\rOriginal text}we will piece together the biggest jigsaw puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.50,0:24:49.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最大的拼圖\N{\rOriginal text}in the history of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.38,0:24:52.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}六百萬個零部件散落在全國各地\N{\rOriginal text}Six million parts spread out around the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:55.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們要對每一個零件 進行組裝 測試 再測試\N{\rOriginal text}and we will assemble, test, and retest every single one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:58.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}直到我們確定阿波羅11號 可以萬無一失地發射\N{\rOriginal text}until we are certain that Apollo 11 will take off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.22,0:25:01.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}並飛向月球 就在...\N{\rOriginal text}without a hitch and head to the moon in...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.77,0:25:02.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利 你說\N{\rOriginal text}Henry, sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:05.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在七個月後\N{\rOriginal text}Seven months. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.65,0:25:06.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}七個月後\N{\rOriginal text}Seven months.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.94,0:25:10.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請幫我恭喜阿波羅11號的宇航員\N{\rOriginal text}Please help me congratulate the astronauts of Apollo 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.07,0:25:14.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗 奧爾德林和柯林斯\N{\rOriginal text}Armstrong, Aldrin and Collins.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:29.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿... 夥計們 你們覺得白宮怎麼樣?\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, hey! How'd you like the White House, boys? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.88,0:25:28.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(月球 我們來了)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.34,0:25:32.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還不錯 只可惜尼爾不讓我偷那裏的瓷器\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, it was all right, except Neil wouldn't let me steal the china.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:39.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 因為在八個月後 等這一切都結束\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Because in eight months, when this is all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.22,0:25:43.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們需要新歷史書 來記載我們在這裏取得的成就時\N{\rOriginal text}and they need new history books to cover what we've accomplished here,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.22,0:25:46.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們每一個人都能說\N{\rOriginal text}each and every single one of you will be able to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.19,0:25:51.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「我做了有史以來最困難的事」 對嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}"I did the hardest thing that has ever been done." Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.11,0:25:52.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.15,0:25:54.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}行動起來 開工\N{\rOriginal text}Let's do it. Let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.70,0:26:01.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}漂亮 說得好 謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}Beautiful. Perfect. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.87,0:26:03.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 長官\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.79,0:26:07.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你說新來的女士 只要做任何你不喜歡的事就通知你\N{\rOriginal text}you said to tell you when the new lady did anything you wouldn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:09.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我身處肯尼迪航天中心\N{\rOriginal text}I'm here at the Kennedy Space Center
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.79,0:26:12.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有幸採訪到副發射主管亨利·斯莫爾斯\N{\rOriginal text}with Deputy Launch Director, Henry Smalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:14.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼回事? 那是我的名字 他盜用了我的名字和職位\N{\rOriginal text}What's going on? That's my name. He's got my name and my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.92,0:26:18.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這段時間對我們所有人來說都很美好 對我來說更具個人感情\N{\rOriginal text}It's been a great time for all of us. You know, for me, this is very personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.09,0:26:19.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我父親是一位空軍士兵\N{\rOriginal text}My father was an airman...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.43,0:26:20.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是誰啊?\N{\rOriginal text}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:22.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}反正不是我 他在服役時犧牲了\N{\rOriginal text}It's not me. he died in the line of duty
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.89,0:26:24.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}當時我還是個孩子 我沒那麼帥\N{\rOriginal text}when I was a child... I'm not that handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.85,0:26:26.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是為了你 老爸\N{\rOriginal text}... so this is for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.02,0:26:27.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真是夠了 聽到這個我很遺憾\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, that's it. So sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.89,0:26:30.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝你的分享 這一定很... 我爸還活著呢\N{\rOriginal text}Thanks for sharing. That must've been... My dad's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.65,0:26:36.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 要怎樣才能約在晚上6點左右呢? 好\N{\rOriginal text}Right. What is it that we can do to sort of make 6:00 p.m.? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.57,0:26:39.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}國家航空航天局公共事務部 我是凱莉·瓊斯\N{\rOriginal text}NASA Public Affairs, this is Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:42.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉 美國廣播公司 想要下周的媒體錄影帶\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, ABC wants next week's press reel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.16,0:26:44.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還想要我們手上最好的阿波羅8號照片\N{\rOriginal text}They also want the best photo we have from the Apollo 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.41,0:26:46.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟他們說 如果讓我們 上晚6點時間段就給他們\N{\rOriginal text}Tell them they can have it if they give us their 6:00 p.m. time slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.91,0:26:49.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}明白 如果你們播放動畫片段\N{\rOriginal text}Got it. If you air an animated segment,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.46,0:26:51.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我能給你們提供獨家的... 非常感謝\N{\rOriginal text}I can offer you an exclusive... Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.75,0:26:54.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你父親是個英雄 你是個英雄 我們非常感激你勤懇地...\N{\rOriginal text}Your father was a hero. You are a hero. We so appreciate you working at...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.55,0:26:57.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是全國廣播公司新聞主管 是 我不管 這人是誰?\N{\rOriginal text}That was the head of NBC News. Yeah, I don't care. Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.42,0:26:59.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝 我們月球上見\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you. See you on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.05,0:27:01.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在公眾眼裏 他是亨利·斯莫爾斯\N{\rOriginal text}To the world, that's Henry Smalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.59,0:27:02.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他不是亨利·斯莫爾斯\N{\rOriginal text}That's not Henry Smalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.80,0:27:04.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 但你跟我說你們不接受採訪\N{\rOriginal text}No, but you told me that your guys don't do interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.85,0:27:06.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以我只能另請新人\N{\rOriginal text}so I had to hire new guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.60,0:27:11.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你讓兩位全球最頂尖的工程師裝窗戶\N{\rOriginal text}You have two of the best engineers on the planet installing a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.81,0:27:14.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}菲爾 你再揮一下錘子 我一定會瘋掉\N{\rOriginal text}Phil, if you hammer one more time, I swear to God I'm gonna lose my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.48,0:27:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}把錘子放下 摘掉該死的工具帶\N{\rOriginal text}Put down the hammer, take your stupid belts off
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.44,0:27:17.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}回去測試\N{\rOriginal text}and get back to testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.49,0:27:20.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}動起來 走了\N{\rOriginal text}On the move. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.70,0:27:22.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這景色絕了吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you believe that view?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.28,0:27:24.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們拿到了阿波羅8號的第一批照片 比我的好\N{\rOriginal text}We got the first photos from Apollo 8. It's better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.66,0:27:26.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}從月球拍的第一張地球照片\N{\rOriginal text}The first shot of the earth from the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.58,0:27:29.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是不是你見過最美的東西?\N{\rOriginal text}Isn't that the most beautiful thing you've ever seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.00,0:27:32.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎麼比我先拿到? 他們稱之為「地出」\N{\rOriginal text}How'd you get this before me? They're calling it "Earthrise."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.13,0:27:34.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這張照片會登上今晚所有新聞的頭條\N{\rOriginal text}It's going to be at the top of every news segment tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.25,0:27:36.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1968年太糟糕了\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, '68 has been such a terrible year.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.00,0:27:39.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}刺殺 可憎的戰爭 我們見證了人類最醜惡的一面\N{\rOriginal text}Assassinations, this heinous war, we've seen the worst of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:42.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這時國家航空航天局公佈這張照片 一個看世界的全新視角\N{\rOriginal text}Now NASA gives us this? A whole new way to see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.47,0:27:46.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我會確保所有人都看到\N{\rOriginal text}And I'm gonna make sure everybody sees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.23,0:27:51.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不能找人冒充別人啊\N{\rOriginal text}You can't just fake people!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.23,0:27:54.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 我是來參加選角的\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, I'm here for the casting. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.23,0:27:58.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是誰? 是你 你這個角色可搶手了\N{\rOriginal text}Who's he? You. You're a juicy part.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.40,0:28:01.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要拍這幾場戲 這裏是角色生平\N{\rOriginal text}So, here's the scenes and the character bio.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.28,0:28:03.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你要扮演的就是這位 所以最好提升一點魅力\N{\rOriginal text}This is the man that you're playing, so you wanna up the charisma a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.78,0:28:05.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我會提升... 明白? 好\N{\rOriginal text}Can do. I'll up the... Okay? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.16,0:28:07.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在朝鮮執行過60次任務? 是的\N{\rOriginal text}Sixty missions in Korea? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.54,0:28:10.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很榮幸 我在朝鮮飛過52次任務\N{\rOriginal text}It's an honor. I flew 52 missions in Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.79,0:28:11.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我取了個整數\N{\rOriginal text}I rounded up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.25,0:28:17.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「我在朝鮮飛過52次任務」 怎麼樣?\N{\rOriginal text}"I flew 52 missions in Korea." How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.42,0:28:19.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什麼? 我會練習一下的\N{\rOriginal text}What? I'll work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.84,0:28:25.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她現在都找好人冒充我了\N{\rOriginal text}She has a fake me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.26,0:28:28.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她已經有了個假的我 她有個假的我 假的你\N{\rOriginal text}She got a fake me. She got a fake me and a fake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.10,0:28:29.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不能冒充你和我 一無所獲\N{\rOriginal text}You can't fake me and you. There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.72,0:28:32.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有莫·伯克斯 我每個字都看過了\N{\rOriginal text}There's no Moe Berkus. I checked every spelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.39,0:28:35.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有個叫莫·伯克斯的打來電話\N{\rOriginal text}I have a Moe Berkus on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.57,0:28:41.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要我來說嗎? 不... 我會很享受的\N{\rOriginal text}Do you want me to talk? Oh, no, no. I'm gonna enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.24,0:28:43.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這將是國家航空航天局史上最快速的解雇\N{\rOriginal text}This is gonna be the fastest firing in NASA's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.91,0:28:47.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 莫 科爾 我聽說你在找我\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, Moe. Cole, I hear you're looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.28,0:28:50.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 凱莉·瓊斯 聘請了演員來假扮國家航空航天局工程師\N{\rOriginal text}I am. Kelly Jones hired actors to play NASA engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.70,0:28:54.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是不可接受的 我要她今天就走人\N{\rOriginal text}It is unacceptable. I want her desk cleared today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.12,0:28:57.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}冷靜點... 好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Calm, calm, calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.84,0:29:01.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}華盛頓的政要們會看電視 阿波羅現在上電視了\N{\rOriginal text}Washington watches TV. Apollo is now on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.88,0:29:03.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每個頻道 每天都播\N{\rOriginal text}Every channel, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.68,0:29:07.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們想登月嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}So, you want to get to the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.26,0:29:09.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我建議你們專心做好本職工作\N{\rOriginal text}I suggest, focus on your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.56,0:29:10.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也讓凱莉做好本職工作\N{\rOriginal text}Let Kelly do hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.43,0:29:14.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果她把你打造成舞會上的焦點\N{\rOriginal text}If she's made you the belle of the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:18.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不妨穿上芭蕾舞裙來跳一段\N{\rOriginal text}why don't you just slip on your tutu and do some dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.82,0:29:27.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}炒掉她了?\N{\rOriginal text}She fired? Mm-mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.28,0:29:31.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們被炒了?\N{\rOriginal text}Are we fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.04,0:29:38.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅8號載著宇航員 博爾曼 洛弗爾和安德斯\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 8, carrying astronauts Borman, Lovell and Anders
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.38,0:29:40.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}由土星5號送入了太空\N{\rOriginal text}was launched into space by a Saturn V.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.71,0:29:44.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每一個電視網都在播放地出照片\N{\rOriginal text}Every single network is airing the Earthrise shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.59,0:29:46.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}會傳遍世界各地\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, it's... it's gonna be everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.72,0:29:49.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我試著畫了幾筆\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I tried a little something on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.47,0:29:52.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但好像效果還不行 不夠吸引人 我們需要一個關聯\N{\rOriginal text}but I just don't think it's working yet. It's not enough. We need a hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.39,0:29:55.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一個把登月和人們日常生活掛鉤的方法\N{\rOriginal text}a way to weave the moon landing into people's everyday lives
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.06,0:29:56.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還得潛移默化\N{\rOriginal text}without them realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.19,0:29:59.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 你們有類似沙拉的東西嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, hi. Do you have anything close to a salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.23,0:30:01.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}漢堡上的醃黃瓜\N{\rOriginal text}Pickles come on a burger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.27,0:30:04.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不過要等一等 阿波羅的新聞一出 生意變好了\N{\rOriginal text}It's gonna be a minute, though. Apollo news has business picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.86,0:30:07.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有很多遊客想來親眼見證歷史\N{\rOriginal text}All the tourists love to come in and see little pieces of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.36,0:30:11.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}見證歷史? 對 比如那支筆\N{\rOriginal text}Pieces of history? Yeah, like... like that pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.41,0:30:14.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1961年 約翰·格倫每晚都來這裏用餐\N{\rOriginal text}John Glenn ate here every night in '61.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.20,0:30:14.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(沃爾菲上太空了)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.62,0:30:17.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他用我們的一支筆來寫飛行手冊\N{\rOriginal text}He would work on his flight manuals, and he'd use one of our pens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.37,0:30:19.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那支筆上過水星6號\N{\rOriginal text}That one ended up on Mercury 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.79,0:30:23.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏是全世界唯一一家 名字上過太空的餐廳\N{\rOriginal text}You're at the only restaurant in the world whose name's been in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.30,0:30:26.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很酷\N{\rOriginal text}That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.51,0:30:34.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}正前方\N{\rOriginal text}And right up ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.18,0:30:36.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是著名的水星火箭\N{\rOriginal text}it's the famous Mercury rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.93,0:30:39.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一定要在這裏拍照 但別站太近\N{\rOriginal text}Be sure to get a picture here, but don't stand too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.94,0:30:41.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}火箭可能會發射\N{\rOriginal text}They might go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.36,0:30:45.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那個週末過後 他就恢復了\N{\rOriginal text}He recovered after that weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.36,0:30:45.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(你能準備好嗎? 距離發射還有171天)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.16,0:30:52.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你每次進房間 大家都會安靜下來 你感到困擾嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Does it bother you that a room dies every time you walk into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.49,0:30:54.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你該待在你那邊的\N{\rOriginal text}You're supposed to stay on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.79,0:30:56.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我想你了\N{\rOriginal text}I missed you. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.04,0:30:57.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我希望你批准我們新的推廣活動\N{\rOriginal text}I'd like you to approve our new ad campaigns.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:30:59.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不如就像上次一樣先斬後奏吧\N{\rOriginal text}Why don't you just sidestep me like you did last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.71,0:31:02.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我想為那些讓你措手不及的採訪道歉\N{\rOriginal text}I wanna apologize for blindsiding you with the interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.71,0:31:04.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有辦法解決我們的資金問題\N{\rOriginal text}I have a fix for our money problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.42,0:31:09.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不接受你的道歉 也不接受這些莫名奇妙的東西\N{\rOriginal text}Well, your apology is rejected, and so is whatever this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.84,0:31:12.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}歐米茄 聽著 這裏不是麥迪遜大道\N{\rOriginal text}Omega. Look, this isn't Madison Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.68,0:31:14.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們不會為這種東西買單 不 免費的\N{\rOriginal text}We don't pay for this stuff. No, it's cost-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.85,0:31:16.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}品牌方能得到錢都買不到的合作機會\N{\rOriginal text}The brands get a tie-in money can't buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.81,0:31:19.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而國家航空航天局 可以潛移默化去影響普通人\N{\rOriginal text}and NASA works its way into the minds of everyday people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.69,0:31:22.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}手錶廣告? 這就是你的絕妙點子?\N{\rOriginal text}A watch ad? That's-That's your big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.77,0:31:24.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}準備好了?\N{\rOriginal text}Ready? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.73,0:31:25.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}牙膏\N{\rOriginal text}Toothpaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.49,0:31:31.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}果珍 「阿波羅宇航員選擇的 能量早餐飲品\N{\rOriginal text}Tang. "The energy breakfast drink chosen for Apollo astronauts
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.36,0:31:33.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}專供登月之旅使用」 月球優惠券?\N{\rOriginal text}on their trip to the moon." Moon coupons?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.66,0:31:36.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我個人最喜歡的要屬這個\N{\rOriginal text}But, my personal favorite,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.83,0:31:39.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鮮果布衣 是吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Fruit of the Loom. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.75,0:31:42.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}宇航員在太空服裏面總得穿點什麼吧?\N{\rOriginal text}The guys gotta wear something under those big suits, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.29,0:31:43.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鮮果布衣真的太能代表航天局了\N{\rOriginal text}Nothing says NASA like Fruit of the Loom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.96,0:31:47.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 我不會把飛船變成飛行廣告牌\N{\rOriginal text}Look, I am not turning this ship into a flying billboard
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.46,0:31:49.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}無論你多麼渴望都不行\N{\rOriginal text}no matter how much you want it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.38,0:31:52.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還有 我們沒時間在發射前測試這些東西\N{\rOriginal text}And by the way, we don't have time to test all this before liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.14,0:31:54.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們不必真的把這些送上太空 只要說說就好\N{\rOriginal text}We don't have to send any of this up into space as long as we say it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.72,0:31:56.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以你打算撒謊?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, so you're gonna lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.14,0:31:58.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這叫推銷 我們不會欺騙顧客\N{\rOriginal text}It's called selling. We're not lying to the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.10,0:32:00.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們在改變他們的思維方式 不 這叫撒謊\N{\rOriginal text}We're changing the way they think. No, it's called lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.31,0:32:03.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有人在你眼裏都只是顧客嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Everyone is just a customer to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.23,0:32:06.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 我知道你是個厲害的廣告精英\N{\rOriginal text}Look, I know that you're a big old fancy ad shark and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.77,0:32:09.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但國家航空航天局 不是能用廣告曲和廣告詞推銷的\N{\rOriginal text}but NASA's not something that you sell with a jingle and a slogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.99,0:32:12.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不知道我們是誰\N{\rOriginal text}You do not know who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.41,0:32:14.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}行 好吧 瑪格麗特·漢密爾頓是誰?\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, okay. Who's Margaret Hamilton?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.95,0:32:16.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}誰? 她是你的手下\N{\rOriginal text}Who? She works here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.99,0:32:19.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有四十萬人和太空計劃有關\N{\rOriginal text}There are 400,000 people that are affiliated
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.41,0:32:21.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}瓊斯女士 她是你的工程師之一\N{\rOriginal text}with this space program, Ms. Jones. She's one of your engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.91,0:32:24.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}喬安·摩根是誰? 她是點火室的\N{\rOriginal text}Who's JoAnn Morgan? She works in the firing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.13,0:32:27.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你問過她當初為什麼接這份工作嗎? 我就問過\N{\rOriginal text}Did you ever ask her why she took this job in the first place? I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.17,0:32:30.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她說因為她的血液裏流的都是火箭燃料\N{\rOriginal text}She says it's because she has rocket fuel in her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.34,0:32:32.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}國家航空航天局不光是個標誌 也代表著人民\N{\rOriginal text}And NASA's not just a logo, it's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.51,0:32:34.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那些每天早上醒來\N{\rOriginal text}People who wake up every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.01,0:32:36.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}決心創造奇跡的人\N{\rOriginal text}and commit to accomplishing the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:39.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}同時跟大家穿著一樣的內衣\N{\rOriginal text}And all while wearing the same underwear as the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.89,0:32:43.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}艾拉 你有任何需要嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Ella, can I help you with anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.07,0:32:51.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.61,0:32:55.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我預估了一下 如果你接受關鍵贊助\N{\rOriginal text}So I ran the projections, and this is what you stand to make
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.32,0:32:57.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能賺到這個數\N{\rOriginal text}if you accept key sponsorships.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.62,0:33:02.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們不能收私人的錢\N{\rOriginal text}We-We can't take private money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.50,0:33:04.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}無所謂的 明白嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}It doesn't matter, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.37,0:33:06.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我即將讓航天局變得非常受歡迎\N{\rOriginal text}I'm about to make NASA so popular
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.17,0:33:09.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}國會終將重新提供資金\N{\rOriginal text}that Congress will finally turn the taps back on around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.00,0:33:12.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只需讓阿姆斯特朗 戴上一塊歐米茄手錶就行?\N{\rOriginal text}And all I have to do is just let Armstrong put on an Omega watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:15.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 如果我們得到資金\N{\rOriginal text}No. If we get the money flowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.18,0:33:17.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那你必須向我證明\N{\rOriginal text}then you've gotta prove to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.68,0:33:20.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可可海灘也有不錯的地方可以吃晚餐\N{\rOriginal text}that Cocoa Beach has a decent place to get dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.40,0:33:29.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}成交 我... 好 成交 太好了 嗚呼\N{\rOriginal text}Deal. I... Yes! Deal! Yes! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.61,0:33:33.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 等等 我得設置底線 手紙不行\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, no, wait. I'm drawing the line at toilet paper though,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.74,0:33:36.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為世人不用知道我們的人用什麼擦屁股\N{\rOriginal text}because the world does not get to know what our guys wipe their ass with.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.70,0:33:38.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真臭\N{\rOriginal text}Well, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.54,0:33:45.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你返回地球後想去度假嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Would you like to go for a vacation when you come back to earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.46,0:33:48.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}根據目前的情況看\N{\rOriginal text}The situation being what it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.13,0:33:50.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我最可能去的地方...\N{\rOriginal text}the place I would most like to go, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.09,0:33:53.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下次把桌子撤掉 沃爾特\N{\rOriginal text}Lose the table next time, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.05,0:33:55.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾看起來 像在做通用電氣的季度盈利報告\N{\rOriginal text}Neil looks like he's giving GE's quarterly profit report.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.80,0:33:57.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們一直用這張桌...\N{\rOriginal text}That's always been our table...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.55,0:33:59.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}電視讓他們走進人們的起居室\N{\rOriginal text}TV brings them in to people's living rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.43,0:34:01.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們應該看起來像家中的客人\N{\rOriginal text}They should look like they belong there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.01,0:34:03.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那意味著我們成功了\N{\rOriginal text}It'd mean that we succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.43,0:34:06.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你還是負責人 沃爾特 別擔心\N{\rOriginal text}You're still in charge, Walter. Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.23,0:34:08.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不過等我幫完忙後\N{\rOriginal text}When I'm done helping though,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.73,0:34:10.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這些人會比披頭士樂隊還火\N{\rOriginal text}those men are gonna be bigger than The Beatles.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:14.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我可以完成99.9%的登月之旅 我很滿意\N{\rOriginal text}I'm getting to go 99.9% of the way there, and that suits me just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.45,0:34:17.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(下一站 月球)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.91,0:34:21.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波羅11號 最危險的航行)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.16,0:34:30.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}家樂氏的那個副總叫什麼? 應該是哈里森·德裏斯科爾\N{\rOriginal text}What's the name of that VP at Kellogg's? I believe it's Harrison Driscoll.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.16,0:34:26.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波羅登月在即)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.83,0:34:31.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 哈里森\N{\rOriginal text}All right, Harrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.75,0:34:36.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不要用「辟啪 笑笑 泡泡」 改用「尼爾 巴茲和邁克」 不錯吧?\N{\rOriginal text}So instead of "Snap, Crackle, Pop," "Neil, Buzz and Mike." It's cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.68,0:34:42.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科爾\N{\rOriginal text}Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.73,0:34:48.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}確保那個不會生銹 亨利 能簽一下這些嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Make sure that doesn't rust, Henry. Can you mark these?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.81,0:34:54.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿... 你看見了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, hey. Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.27,0:34:55.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你沒看見那隻貓?\N{\rOriginal text}You didn't see the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:34:59.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}果珍的瓶子再推近些\N{\rOriginal text}Go closer on the Tang bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.95,0:35:02.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}字體再大些 放上培根和雞蛋\N{\rOriginal text}Make the font bigger and put bacon with the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.95,0:35:05.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別忘了 我們推銷的是美國\N{\rOriginal text}Let's not forget, we're selling America, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:10.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「彼得潘花生醬 絲滑到飛起 此醬只應天上有」\N{\rOriginal text}"Peter Pan Peanut Butter. Peanut butter that's out-of-this-world smooth."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.42,0:35:13.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「哈蘇 以他們的視角看世界」\N{\rOriginal text}"Hasselblad. See the world the way they do."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.71,0:35:15.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拉裏 這是歐米茄的好機會\N{\rOriginal text}Larry, this is Omega's big chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.80,0:35:18.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在每一塊超霸的背面 直到永遠\N{\rOriginal text}On the back of every Speedmaster till the end of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.68,0:35:20.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(宇航員登上月球時將佩戴歐米茄手錶)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.55,0:35:23.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「第一塊被戴上月球的手錶」 對吧?\N{\rOriginal text}"The first watch worn on the moon." Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.39,0:35:25.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}現在我們得把它立起來\N{\rOriginal text}Now we just gotta stand her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.85,0:35:27.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一切都將是值得的\N{\rOriginal text}It's all gonna be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.31,0:35:32.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(美國靠阿波羅11號取得領先)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.57,0:35:39.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿... 你佔了我的車位 我們在為凱莉佈景\N{\rOriginal text}Hey. Hey! You're in my spot. We're setting up a shot for Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.46,0:35:54.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們的阿波羅11號任務有三位宇航員\N{\rOriginal text}We've got three astronauts on the Apollo 11 mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.09,0:35:57.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們站在三輛漂亮的美國汽車前\N{\rOriginal text}There they are in front of three beautiful American cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.76,0:35:59.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真棒\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, this is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:00.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們必須立刻前往測試樓\N{\rOriginal text}You gotta be in the test facility right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.55,0:36:01.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟凱莉說\N{\rOriginal text}Talk to Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.51,0:36:03.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉說我們花1塊就能開走科爾維特\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly said we could take a Corvette home for a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.39,0:36:04.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你來啦 1美元?\N{\rOriginal text}There you are. A dollar?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.43,0:36:06.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我需要佔用他們15分鐘而已\N{\rOriginal text}I'm gonna need them for 15 minutes, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.18,0:36:08.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我15分鐘前就需要他們了 凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}I needed them 15 minutes ago, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.27,0:36:10.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你知道他們穿的宇航服有多貴嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You know how expensive those suits are?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.31,0:36:14.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別擔心 他只是發射主管\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, don't worry. It's just the launch director.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.94,0:36:17.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月艙的樣子很怪 凱利先生 它的原理是什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}This strange looking bird, the LEM, Mr. Kelly. How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.98,0:36:20.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是讓人\N{\rOriginal text}Well, this is a spacecraft that's used
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.28,0:36:22.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}著陸到月球表面的飛船\N{\rOriginal text}to take men down to the lunar surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.99,0:36:25.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月艙裏三位宇航員中的兩位...\N{\rOriginal text}And two of the three astronauts in the LEM...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.95,0:36:33.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飛行指揮 我們錯過了目標 正飄向廣袤的虛空\N{\rOriginal text}Flight, we missed target and are drifting into the vast abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.92,0:36:39.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們死了 再來 是\N{\rOriginal text}And we're dead. Again. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.05,0:36:41.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}著陸前30秒耗盡了燃料\N{\rOriginal text}Ran out of fuel 30 seconds before touchdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.22,0:36:42.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 但是著陸本身不錯\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, but the landing, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.51,0:36:44.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很順利 很好 俯仰角度很好 繼續\N{\rOriginal text}it was smooth... It was good. Great pitch. Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.43,0:36:45.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們倆撒謊的技術真爛\N{\rOriginal text}You're both bad liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.89,0:36:49.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾 邁克 巴茲 能再為瓊斯女士 和歐米茄多拍一張照片嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Neil, Mike, Buzz, if I can get one more photo for Ms. Jones and Omega?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.47,0:36:50.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哥們 你誰啊?\N{\rOriginal text}Who are you, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.77,0:36:55.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 舉起手錶 小伙子們\N{\rOriginal text}All right, watches up, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.86,0:36:57.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}給歐米茄來個微笑\N{\rOriginal text}And smile for Omega.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.24,0:37:07.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是戴維斯 我打擾到你了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Davis. Am I interrupting?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.08,0:37:11.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一直在打擾 你面前應該有個盒子\N{\rOriginal text}Always. There should be a box in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.79,0:37:13.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不如打開看看?\N{\rOriginal text}Why don't you open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.71,0:37:20.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}歐米茄感謝你的服務\N{\rOriginal text}Omega thanks you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:22.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的宇航員們在電視上大出風頭\N{\rOriginal text}Your boys are all over TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.88,0:37:28.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}資金又開始流入了 所以... 共進晚餐?\N{\rOriginal text}the taps are flowing again. So... dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.85,0:37:33.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 卡納維拉爾碼頭 5點\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Canaveral Pier. Five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.44,0:37:35.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴著手錶來\N{\rOriginal text}Wear your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.19,0:37:40.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下午3點是他們播放採訪的 最佳時段 也是最後一個\N{\rOriginal text}3:00 p.m. is their best and final time slot to air the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.36,0:37:43.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}播阿姆斯特朗的獨家採訪? 下午3點是給小孩和閒人看的\N{\rOriginal text}For an exclusive with Armstrong? 3:00 p.m. is for children and deadbeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.70,0:37:46.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們說有戰爭方面的突發新聞\N{\rOriginal text}They said they have breaking news from the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.37,0:37:50.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}敵軍規模未知\N{\rOriginal text}Unknown size enemy force.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.24,0:37:52.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}敵軍傷亡人數不詳\N{\rOriginal text}Enemy casualties are unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.62,0:37:54.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但大家都看到過到底是怎麼回事\N{\rOriginal text}but you've seen how it really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.33,0:37:56.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讓阿波羅任務一直有新聞的努力失敗了\N{\rOriginal text}So much for keeping Apollo back in the news cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.46,0:37:58.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}英雄主義 危險 恐懼 全部融為一體\N{\rOriginal text}Heroism, danger, fear, all rolled into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.92,0:38:00.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}無法用語言形容\N{\rOriginal text}Words don't describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.67,0:38:04.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是哥倫比亞廣播公司新聞台的 理查德·思雷爾克德 柬埔寨邊境附近報道\N{\rOriginal text}Richard Threlkeld, CBS News. Near the Cambodian border.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.43,0:38:10.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝你 斯科蒂船長 感謝\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you, Captain Scotty. Appreciate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.31,0:38:12.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.31,0:38:14.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你對女士可真是一毛不拔\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you spare no expense on a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.23,0:38:15.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘗嘗看嘛\N{\rOriginal text}Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.64,0:38:17.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蝦 蛋黃醬 麵包\N{\rOriginal text}Shrimp, mayo, bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.10,0:38:19.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這恰好是方圓百里之內最美味的一餐\N{\rOriginal text}And that happens to be the best meal in a hundred miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.36,0:38:25.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我沒說錯吧\N{\rOriginal text}Mmm. Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.61,0:38:28.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我怎麼不知道這地方?\N{\rOriginal text}How'd I not know about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.24,0:38:30.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是所有人都喜歡打廣告\N{\rOriginal text}Not everybody likes to advertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.16,0:38:33.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}說得妙 有兩下子嘛\N{\rOriginal text}Nice one. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.21,0:38:41.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是火箭發射的地方 就是那裏\N{\rOriginal text}That's where the rocket will launch out of. Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.09,0:38:48.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你戴那塊手錶戴可真好看 你戴著很合適\N{\rOriginal text}That watch looks great on you. You wear it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.18,0:38:53.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.39,0:38:59.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那天晚上我在酒吧裏跟你說...\N{\rOriginal text}That night at the bar, what I said to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.85,0:39:01.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的目光無法從我身上挪開\N{\rOriginal text}That you couldn't take your eyes off me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.48,0:39:03.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是你見過最美的女人\N{\rOriginal text}and I was the most beautiful woman that you'd ever seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.86,0:39:06.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 就是這句 這... 對\N{\rOriginal text}Y-Yeah, that part. That... Yes. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:08.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是我衝動了\N{\rOriginal text}It was impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.49,0:39:11.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是對陌生人說的話 可我們現在共事了\N{\rOriginal text}It was meant for a stranger, and we're working together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.45,0:39:13.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只是不希望你認為我...\N{\rOriginal text}So, I just don't want you to think that I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.87,0:39:14.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對我有意思?\N{\rOriginal text}Interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.25,0:39:18.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只是想把話說清楚\N{\rOriginal text}I just wanted to clear the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.17,0:39:21.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 說得很清楚\N{\rOriginal text}Oh. Well, the air was clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:22.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好\N{\rOriginal text}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.38,0:39:33.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有個想法 對 那話只適用30秒\N{\rOriginal text}I had a thought. Yeah. It was perfect for 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.10,0:39:35.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有哪個電視網是全天候報道的?\N{\rOriginal text}What are the networks covering night and day?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.81,0:39:37.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你覺得我有時間看電視嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You think I have time to watch TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:41.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}越南 他們直接從前線報道\N{\rOriginal text}Vietnam. They're broadcasting straight from the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.19,0:39:43.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人們已經不想只聽新聞了\N{\rOriginal text}And people don't want to just hear the news anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.02,0:39:44.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們想直擊新聞現場\N{\rOriginal text}They wanna see it in the making.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.65,0:39:46.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.16,0:39:56.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不妨就讓他們看\N{\rOriginal text}Why not let 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.16,0:39:56.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(登月現場直播 阿波羅11號)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.29,0:39:58.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你想在登月艙裏放個電視直播攝像機?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you want to put a live television camera on the LEM?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.79,0:40:00.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.04,0:40:01.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的人在太空裏努力活命\N{\rOriginal text}My guys are trying to survive up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.67,0:40:03.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒時間學如何拍電影\N{\rOriginal text}They don't have time to figure out how to film a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.63,0:40:06.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們替他們學 他們只需對準目標拍攝即可\N{\rOriginal text}We'll figure it out for 'em. All they have to do is point and shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.13,0:40:08.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不明白 這是後勤方面的噩夢\N{\rOriginal text}You don't get it. It's a logistical nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.51,0:40:11.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}問題涉及電力 儲存空間 重量\N{\rOriginal text}There's power issues, storage, weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:13.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}甚至沒有攝像機能在太空裏工作\N{\rOriginal text}There's not even a camera that would work up there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.18,0:40:16.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為夜晚溫度是零下129攝氏度 白天超過121攝氏度\N{\rOriginal text}'cause it's negative 200 degrees at night and over 250 degrees during the daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.31,0:40:18.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你能想像看直播的情景嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you imagine seeing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.52,0:40:21.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不能 我剛說了這不可能\N{\rOriginal text}No. I just said it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.98,0:40:23.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 這就是重點\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. That's the point. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.73,0:40:25.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這將是有史以來最偉大的電視節目\N{\rOriginal text}It would be the greatest televised event ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.82,0:40:27.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你認為這是個綜藝節目嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you think this is a game show?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.15,0:40:29.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘇聯人沒有播出\N{\rOriginal text}There is a very good reason
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.82,0:40:32.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們在太空行走是有充分理由的\N{\rOriginal text}why the Soviets aren't broadcasting their space walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.66,0:40:34.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為蘇聯是守口如瓶的獨裁政權國\N{\rOriginal text}Because they're a tight-lipped dictatorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:35.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 我們不是 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, that's not us. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.99,0:40:38.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們取得成功 是舉國成功\N{\rOriginal text}When we succeed, we do it as a nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.04,0:40:40.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們遭遇失敗 是舉國悲痛 對\N{\rOriginal text}And when we fail, we grieve as a nation. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.41,0:40:42.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這就是作為美國人的意義所在\N{\rOriginal text}That's what it means to be American.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.21,0:40:44.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別跟我說作為美國人意味著什麼\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, stop telling me what it means to be an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.75,0:40:47.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們當中只有一個人一輩子在報效祖國\N{\rOriginal text}There's only one of us here that has served their country their entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.59,0:40:53.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 登月艙裏不會放攝像機的\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. We're not putting the camera on the LEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.56,0:41:00.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是認真的 不放\N{\rOriginal text}I mean it. We're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.06,0:41:04.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們會放的\N{\rOriginal text}We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.94,0:41:08.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(壓力點)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.57,0:41:12.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有更多燃料 他不可能成功\N{\rOriginal text}There's no way he can do it without more fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.57,0:41:18.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讓他再測一次 好\N{\rOriginal text}Have him run it again. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.08,0:41:27.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我時間很緊 什麼事?\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. [sighs] I'm on a tight schedule. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.29,0:41:31.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉跟我說了攝像機的點子 我們很喜歡\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly briefed me on the camera idea, and we like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:33.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常喜歡\N{\rOriginal text}We like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.22,0:41:35.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她說錯了 我們做不到\N{\rOriginal text}She misspoke. We can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.14,0:41:38.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}根本沒有這種科技\N{\rOriginal text}There is no such technology that even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.51,0:41:40.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其實有 你知道嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Actually it does. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.72,0:41:43.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是國防部設計的\N{\rOriginal text}The Department of Defense designed this
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.89,0:41:47.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}為了夜間尋找在越南被擊落的飛行員\N{\rOriginal text}to find downed fighter pilots in Vietnam at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.31,0:41:51.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 這是機密 但國防部會給你使用\N{\rOriginal text}Now, it's classified but the DOD is going to let you use it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.94,0:41:53.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}只要沒人知道它是什麼即可\N{\rOriginal text}as long as nobody knows what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.78,0:41:55.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}絕對沒有空間裝這麼重的設備\N{\rOriginal text}There's absolutely no space for equipment that heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.95,0:41:57.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}老天 我們連螺絲釘都稱重\N{\rOriginal text}We are weighing screws for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.70,0:41:59.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什麼... 這也就7公斤吧\N{\rOriginal text}What... I mean, what is this, 15 pounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.58,0:42:01.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 那就用輕一些的螺絲釘\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. So, just, like, lighter screws.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.45,0:42:03.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們在試用另一個燃料單元\N{\rOriginal text}We're trying for another fuel cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.37,0:42:08.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好讓我們的人登月後 依然有足夠的燃料發射\N{\rOriginal text}So our men, when they get to the moon, they still have enough fuel to lift off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.17,0:42:11.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她所有的餿主意當中 這個是最糟糕的\N{\rOriginal text}Out of all her bad ideas, this one is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.42,0:42:14.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其實總統很喜歡這個點子\N{\rOriginal text}Actually, the president loves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.84,0:42:17.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以現在這就是個好主意\N{\rOriginal text}So, now it's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:20.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟你用簡單的話說吧 科爾\N{\rOriginal text}So, let me put it to you simply, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.14,0:42:22.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}找個辦法把這東西放進那東西\N{\rOriginal text}Find a way to put this on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.89,0:42:25.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是命令 頂頭老大下達的\N{\rOriginal text}This is an order. From the tippy top.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.57,0:42:40.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}唐 斯圖 請到這裏來\N{\rOriginal text}Don, Stu. Can you come in here, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.58,0:42:46.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}謝謝 別什麼事都鬧彆扭\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you. Let's not make everything so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.92,0:42:52.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請幫瓊斯小姐把這個絕密攝像機拆出來\N{\rOriginal text}Please help Miss Jones strip this top secret camera down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.17,0:42:54.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不希望他們知道這是絕密\N{\rOriginal text}I don't want 'em to know it's top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.34,0:42:55.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}現在他們知道了\N{\rOriginal text}Well, now they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.42,0:42:57.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請把這個絕密攝像機拆出來\N{\rOriginal text}Please strip this top secret camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.26,0:43:00.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}裝在登月艙上 以備直播\N{\rOriginal text}Mount it onto the LEM for live broadcasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.80,0:43:04.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科爾 還有一件事\N{\rOriginal text}Cole. One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.35,0:43:09.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上周 一架中情局的間諜飛機拍到幾張\N{\rOriginal text}Last week, a CIA spy plane took some surveillance photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.31,0:43:12.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘇聯新型N1火箭的照片\N{\rOriginal text}of the new Russian N1 rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.11,0:43:13.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}國會看到了\N{\rOriginal text}And Congress saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.82,0:43:16.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有些議員對最後一輪撥款\N{\rOriginal text}and some of the members are having cold feet
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.69,0:43:19.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}產生了疑慮\N{\rOriginal text}about the final round of funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.36,0:43:21.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們還有好幾個月才能贏下登月競賽\N{\rOriginal text}We're months away from winning this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.28,0:43:23.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我會讓他們來這裏參觀\N{\rOriginal text}I'm gonna send them down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.03,0:43:25.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你要說服他們稍安勿躁\N{\rOriginal text}and you're gonna convince them to sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.08,0:43:28.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我... 來寫幾個和他們談話的要點\N{\rOriginal text}No. I'm... I'm gonna write up some talking points.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.63,0:43:39.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別往心裏去\N{\rOriginal text}Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.76,0:43:43.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飛行員和重力對抗 這是他們的天性\N{\rOriginal text}Pilots fight gravity. It's part of their nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.45,0:44:06.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利?\N{\rOriginal text}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.71,0:44:13.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 很高興你不是科爾\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I'm... I'm glad you're not Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.67,0:44:14.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是\N{\rOriginal text}Oh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.25,0:44:16.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他不喜歡我吸煙\N{\rOriginal text}He don't like me smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.92,0:44:18.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼 你怕他會給你下禁足令?\N{\rOriginal text}What, are you worried he's gonna ground you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.76,0:44:26.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我... 去年做了緊急搭橋手術\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, no. I, uh... I had emergency bypass surgery last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.26,0:44:29.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 那個混蛋非常頑固 非要我活下去\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. That son of a bitch. He's hell-bent on keeping me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.81,0:44:31.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉 我不知道\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.52,0:44:33.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 這裏沒人知道\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Nobody here does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.44,0:44:34.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除了科爾\N{\rOriginal text}Just Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.44,0:44:40.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 他到醫院來 安慰了我太太三天\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. He came to the hospital and held my wife's hand for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.32,0:44:44.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 我們認識很久了\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. It's a long way from the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.12,0:44:49.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}當時那小子剛從朝鮮回來\N{\rOriginal text}Kid had just got back from Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.12,0:44:53.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是空軍最優秀的飛行員\N{\rOriginal text}The top pilot in the Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.08,0:44:56.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}銀星勳章 飛行十字勳章\N{\rOriginal text}Silver Star. Flying Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.67,0:45:01.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們當時選宇航員時 他在愛德華茲空軍基地是頭號人選\N{\rOriginal text}He was first in line at Edwards when they were looking for astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.30,0:45:04.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但他最後沒能入選\N{\rOriginal text}But, uh, he ended up not making the cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.43,0:45:10.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}為什麼? 是他的脾氣吧\N{\rOriginal text}So, what got him? It was his temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.39,0:45:14.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 是他的心臟\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. His heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.48,0:45:15.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}醫生發現他有心房顫動\N{\rOriginal text}Doc found an A-fib.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.86,0:45:20.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這個小毛病足以讓他無法參加太空計劃\N{\rOriginal text}A little thing but enough to keep him out of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.74,0:45:24.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最優秀的飛行員科爾·戴維斯 卻永遠無法上太空\N{\rOriginal text}Cole Davis is the best pilot who will never get to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.13,0:45:43.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我在過去15年裏天天看這個景色\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I've been looking at this view every day for the last 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.34,0:45:48.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但最近我有種第一次看到的感覺\N{\rOriginal text}But lately, it's like I'm seeing it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.85,0:45:54.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅1號給這裏留下了巨大的陰影\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 1 cast a big shadow on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.69,0:46:00.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}重新看到一些光明真好\N{\rOriginal text}It's nice to have some light back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.28,0:46:05.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.58,0:46:12.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 我總看到科爾每天晚上開車去那邊\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, I keep seeing Cole drive out there every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.58,0:46:15.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他在做什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.59,0:46:20.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}做園藝\N{\rOriginal text}Gardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.19,0:47:22.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(34號發射場)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.19,0:47:25.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波羅1號乘組的精神永垂不朽)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.92,0:47:43.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}準備好了嗎? 好了\N{\rOriginal text}You ready? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.55,0:47:52.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 聽著 我們... 帶參議員參觀一下\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Look, we just... We give the senator a tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.89,0:47:56.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們好好哄他30分鐘 把這個地方運營下去\N{\rOriginal text}We play nice for 30 minutes. We keep the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.27,0:47:58.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 行吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.81,0:48:01.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼了? 它在那裏\N{\rOriginal text}What? She's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.60,0:48:02.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別... 跑 不...\N{\rOriginal text}Don't run. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.77,0:48:04.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}千萬別跑 別... 等等 閉嘴\N{\rOriginal text}Just don't run. Don't... Wait. [shushing] Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.65,0:48:06.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 你看 你把它嚇跑了\N{\rOriginal text}No. See, you scared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.78,0:48:07.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我剛吃過東西\N{\rOriginal text}I just ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.99,0:48:16.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利 快...\N{\rOriginal text}Henry, come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.46,0:48:22.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我討厭那隻貓\N{\rOriginal text}I hate that cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.67,0:48:25.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我懂你的意思\N{\rOriginal text}I see what y... you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.09,0:48:28.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這... 貓真討厭 你看到它看我的眼神了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}That's an asshole cat. Did you see the look it gave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.63,0:48:30.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它在嘲諷我\N{\rOriginal text}It's just taunting me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.47,0:48:33.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是什麼? 是貓食\N{\rOriginal text}What is that? That's cat food.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.85,0:48:36.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有人在餵它 是誰?\N{\rOriginal text}Somebody's feeding that thing. Who's doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.10,0:48:38.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}找出來 立刻查出是誰 立刻炒掉\N{\rOriginal text}Find them. [pants] Find them immediately, and fire them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.98,0:48:41.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴維斯先生 長官 霍普參議員來了\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis. Sir, uh, Senator Hopp is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.56,0:48:43.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 怎麼了? 你看起來很帥\N{\rOriginal text}All right. What? You look fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.27,0:48:44.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}參議員\N{\rOriginal text}Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.94,0:48:46.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你好 戴維斯先生 參議員 我很榮幸\N{\rOriginal text}Hello, Mr. Davis. Senator. What an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.73,0:48:49.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很榮幸 幸會 先生 幸會\N{\rOriginal text}It's an honor and a pleasure. Very nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.36,0:48:54.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅11號太空艙已經運達\N{\rOriginal text}Well, the Apollo 11 capsule has arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.37,0:48:57.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}下周 我們會把它裝在土星5號火箭上\N{\rOriginal text}and next week, we will be attaching it to the Saturn V rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.83,0:49:01.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也就是發射升空 帶我們離開地球大氣層的那個火箭\N{\rOriginal text}And that gets us off the ground and out of earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.04,0:49:05.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這些都很了不起 但我得直說\N{\rOriginal text}Well, that's all very impressive, but I have to be up-front.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.84,0:49:09.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}佐治亞州今年洪水氾濫\N{\rOriginal text}Georgia had some devastating floods this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.13,0:49:12.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要投票把這筆錢用於賑災\N{\rOriginal text}And I'm voting to put this money toward our relief fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.47,0:49:14.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這似乎有點自私 不是嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}That seems a little selfish, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.05,0:49:16.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你說什麼? 就是一種說法\N{\rOriginal text}Excuse me? Uh, that's a figure of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.97,0:49:19.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是這個意思 我的大多數投票人認為\N{\rOriginal text}Here's what he means. My voters mostly think
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.60,0:49:22.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們在登月計劃上花費過多\N{\rOriginal text}we are overspending on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.23,0:49:23.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有意思 因為當我... 喲呼\N{\rOriginal text}That's funny, because... Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.85,0:49:25.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不好意思 霍普參議員\N{\rOriginal text}Excuse me. Senator Hopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.94,0:49:28.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你可能不記得我了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you probably don't remember me,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.36,0:49:31.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你在我大二時來我學校做過演講\N{\rOriginal text}but you spoke at my sophomore year of college.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.53,0:49:33.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}佐治亞理工學院 1955級\N{\rOriginal text}Georgia Tech. '55.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.70,0:49:34.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你是個大黃蜂校友?\N{\rOriginal text}You're a Buzz?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.95,0:49:37.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 先生 我當然記得\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, sir. Of course I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.08,0:49:39.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那天 你的話激勵了我\N{\rOriginal text}Your words inspired me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.29,0:49:43.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你說「承諾意味著忠於一項事業」\N{\rOriginal text}You said, "Commitment means staying loyal to a cause."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.21,0:49:46.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兩年後 我以優異的成績畢業 現在我負責這個部門\N{\rOriginal text}Two years later, I graduated with honors. Now I run this department.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.42,0:49:50.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}1962年 你曾說過 你無論如何\N{\rOriginal text}You know, in '62 you said that you would fight
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.13,0:49:53.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}都會為肯尼迪的夢想而奮鬥\N{\rOriginal text}for Kennedy's dream no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.17,0:49:56.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道登月任務在當時比現在受歡迎\N{\rOriginal text}I know that the moon mission was more popular back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.22,0:49:59.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但如果那個激勵我 在國家航空航天局工作的人\N{\rOriginal text}but it would be just a shame
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.35,0:50:03.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒能照當年的那些話去做\N{\rOriginal text}if the man whose words inspired me to work at NASA
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.60,0:50:06.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就太可惜了\N{\rOriginal text}didn't live by those very same words.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.69,0:50:12.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那就太可惜了 不是嗎? 先生 你真是個了不起的人\N{\rOriginal text}It would be a shame, wouldn't it? Sir, you are just such a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.86,0:50:14.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常感謝\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you so much. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.03,0:50:15.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真了不起\N{\rOriginal text}You are a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.41,0:50:17.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她可真是個佐治亞州甜心美女\N{\rOriginal text}Isn't she just a wonderful Georgia peach here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.49,0:50:18.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 是\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my. Oh. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.57,0:50:20.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你嘴真甜 是的\N{\rOriginal text}You are so sweet. Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.74,0:50:24.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我帶你來一次貴賓級的參觀吧 這是他們的保密項目\N{\rOriginal text}Let me take you on the special VIP tour they didn't tell you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.75,0:50:26.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好啊 太好了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, I'd love that. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.71,0:50:28.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你會陪我一起參觀嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you go on this tour with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.71,0:50:30.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}當然會\N{\rOriginal text}I absolutely will.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.25,0:50:31.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真好\N{\rOriginal text}That's so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.88,0:50:33.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她都熱淚盈眶了 真嚇人\N{\rOriginal text}She teared up. I mean, it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.63,0:50:36.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}揮手微笑\N{\rOriginal text}Wave and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.01,0:50:39.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜拜\N{\rOriginal text}Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.56,0:50:45.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太空計劃不光臃腫又混亂\N{\rOriginal text}The space program is not only a bloated mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.39,0:50:49.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅號還是對上帝\N{\rOriginal text}but Apollo flies in the face of our creator
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.40,0:50:53.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}和我國國父的不敬 我想提醒大家 我們不...\N{\rOriginal text}and the true father of this country. I would remind you that we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.61,0:50:58.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們搞定了霍普 還需要兩票 看起來不會是范寧了\N{\rOriginal text}We landed Hopp. We need two more votes. Looks like it's not gonna be Vanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.57,0:51:02.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}絕對不是范寧 接下來是庫克參議員\N{\rOriginal text}Definitely not Vanning. Next, we have Senator Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.20,0:51:04.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}庫克有點嚇人 我實話實說\N{\rOriginal text}Cook's a little scary. I'm not gonna lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.04,0:51:05.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是冷戰時期的保守派\N{\rOriginal text}He's a Cold War conservative.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.91,0:51:10.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他擔心我們的預算 會從國防部的武器研發經費裏出\N{\rOriginal text}He's worried that our budget takes away from weapons development at the DOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.25,0:51:14.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 參議員 有了N1火箭\N{\rOriginal text}Now, Senator, with the N1 rocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.30,0:51:16.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘇聯人還是有可能搶在我們前面登月\N{\rOriginal text}the Russians still could land on the moon before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.72,0:51:18.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們接下來要向你展示的最新情報\N{\rOriginal text}What we're about to show you is our most recent intel
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.76,0:51:20.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是他們登月後計劃建造的東西\N{\rOriginal text}on what they plan to build if they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.02,0:51:28.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這些是照片? 不是 先生\N{\rOriginal text}And these are photos? No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.31,0:51:31.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是概念畫 描繪可能的未來\N{\rOriginal text}Those are, uh, renderings of a possible future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.40,0:51:32.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}未來的照片?\N{\rOriginal text}Future photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.15,0:51:37.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是個激光炮?\N{\rOriginal text}Is that a laser?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.15,0:51:39.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它正對著地球開火 先生\N{\rOriginal text}It's going towards earth, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.03,0:51:42.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}它叫什麼? 「要你命月球激光大殺器」 先生\N{\rOriginal text}What are they calling it? "Killer Lunar Laser Eliminator," sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.74,0:51:46.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「要你命月球激光大殺器」? 是 先生\N{\rOriginal text}"Killer Lunar Laser Eliminator"? Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.71,0:51:48.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}見鬼 厲害了\N{\rOriginal text}Damn it. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.71,0:51:51.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最後還有赫奇斯參議員\N{\rOriginal text}And, finally, we have Senator Hedges.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.17,0:51:53.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他一直是阿波羅的粉絲\N{\rOriginal text}Now, he's always been a fan of Apollo,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.42,0:51:57.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但州政黨給他施壓 叫他不得撥款\N{\rOriginal text}but he's getting pressure from his state party not to fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.72,0:52:00.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他連呼吸都要對著媒體的鏡頭\N{\rOriginal text}He can't take in oxygen without a camera pointed at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.34,0:52:03.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我們就去請點扛攝像機的朋友來\N{\rOriginal text}and we're about to have a few of those around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.85,0:52:05.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有什麼問題嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.01,0:52:06.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有 女士\N{\rOriginal text}No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.81,0:52:08.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我們去搞定他吧\N{\rOriginal text}Well, let's get him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.35,0:52:12.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大家好\N{\rOriginal text}Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.40,0:52:17.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}先生們\N{\rOriginal text}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.49,0:52:20.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 很高興能故地重遊 各位\N{\rOriginal text}It's... It's... It's great to be back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.61,0:52:23.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們知道我有多喜歡阿波羅計劃\N{\rOriginal text}You know how much I love the Apollo program.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.04,0:52:30.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}參議員 阿波羅10號只會繞月飛行\N{\rOriginal text}Senator. Apollo 10 will just be orbiting the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.71,0:52:34.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但能給我們帶來 11號在月球著陸的關鍵信息\N{\rOriginal text}But it's gonna get us information critical for the touchdown of 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.29,0:52:36.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}比如著陸條件和地點 了不起\N{\rOriginal text}Like landing conditions and location. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.59,0:52:39.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們為你準備了專座 參議員 在你的支持者中間\N{\rOriginal text}And we've a special seat for you here, Senator, amongst your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.09,0:52:40.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}為我嗎? 謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}For me? Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.34,0:52:44.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅發射控制中心 現在可以開始\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo launch control, and we are go on the countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.72,0:52:47.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅10號登月任務的倒計時了\N{\rOriginal text}for the Apollo 10 lunar mission at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.56,0:52:53.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}點火程序啟動\N{\rOriginal text}We have ignition sequence start.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.90,0:52:57.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}五 四 三 二...\N{\rOriginal text}Five, four, three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.44,0:53:00.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有引擎啟動\N{\rOriginal text}All engines running.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.87,0:53:10.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射 火箭升空\N{\rOriginal text}Liftoff. We have liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.62,0:53:12.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}現在是整點後49分\N{\rOriginal text}Forty-nine minutes past the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.25,0:53:15.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射塔已分離...\N{\rOriginal text}Tower clear. Tower clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.04,0:53:17.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}休斯敦 交給你了\N{\rOriginal text}Houston, she's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.86,0:53:45.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}壯觀的發射 我都等不及回來看阿波羅11號了\N{\rOriginal text}Glorious launch. Can't wait to be right back here for Apollo 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.45,0:53:48.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們非常感謝你的支持 參議員\N{\rOriginal text}We cannot thank you enough for your support, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.03,0:53:50.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有件事會麻煩你們一下\N{\rOriginal text}It's gonna cost you more than a pair of binoculars.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.37,0:53:53.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我欠老家做新聞的人一個人情\N{\rOriginal text}I owe a favor to the news fellas back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.62,0:53:57.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我希望你能接受他們的出鏡採訪\N{\rOriginal text}I'd like you to give them an on-camera interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.63,0:54:01.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}參議員 我是最不適合出鏡的人了\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, Senator, I'm the very last person that you want in front of a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.01,0:54:03.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 不接受採訪的\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, I d... I don't do interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.09,0:54:06.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但為你可以破例 赫奇斯參議員 我們很樂意\N{\rOriginal text}Except for you, Senator Hedges. We would be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.39,0:54:08.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這女士很機智\N{\rOriginal text}Smart lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.93,0:54:11.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}晚安 晚安\N{\rOriginal text}Good night. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.64,0:54:15.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.27,0:54:17.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒事的\N{\rOriginal text}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:20.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一切盡在掌握\N{\rOriginal text}Got it all under control. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.99,0:54:27.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(好樣的 阿波羅)
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.43,0:54:50.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 嘿\N{\rOriginal text}Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.93,0:54:52.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你也可以休息一晚的\N{\rOriginal text}You're entitled to a night off too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.81,0:54:56.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我若休息 那就是睡覺\N{\rOriginal text}If I am, it's to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.31,0:54:58.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真的有家嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you actually have a house?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.44,0:55:00.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我還以為你在辦公室睡呢\N{\rOriginal text}I thought you slept at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.15,0:55:04.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 通常是 但... 我有時和珍妮一起睡\N{\rOriginal text}Well, yeah. Usually. But, uh... Well, I mean, sometimes I sleep with Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.82,0:55:08.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 是 她一定很棒\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, yeah. Right. Oh. I'm sure she's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.28,0:55:10.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}珍妮嗎? 對 確實\N{\rOriginal text}Jenny? Yeah. She... She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.16,0:55:15.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}想認識一下嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You wanna meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.91,0:55:17.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好啊 好 珍妮會喜歡你的 來\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Yeah. She'll love you. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.93,0:55:31.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}珍妮 這是凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Jenny. Jenny, uh, this is Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.68,0:55:33.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉 這就是珍妮\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, meet Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.10,0:55:36.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跟我戰爭中開的那架一樣\N{\rOriginal text}She's just like the one I flew in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.23,0:55:40.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我把它放在這裏 方便在週末開出去兜兜風 省時間\N{\rOriginal text}Keep her here so I can get my flight hours on the weekends. Saves time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.02,0:55:44.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很漂亮\N{\rOriginal text}She's quite a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.86,0:55:46.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.07,0:55:51.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}想飛一圈嗎? 不了\N{\rOriginal text}Wanna go up? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.57,0:55:52.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你確定? 確定\N{\rOriginal text}You sure? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.49,0:55:55.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 來吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.45,0:55:57.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我帶你看第二美的景色\N{\rOriginal text}Show you the second-best view.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.80,0:56:15.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看見那些深色的部分了嗎? 看見了\N{\rOriginal text}You see those dark parts there? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.18,0:56:16.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們稱之為「月海」\N{\rOriginal text}We call them the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.56,0:56:19.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}月海裏的重力更強一些 所以...\N{\rOriginal text}The gravity is stronger in the seas, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.98,0:56:23.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們研究過在每一片月海裏著陸的情況\N{\rOriginal text}We've looked to land in, uh, pretty much every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.61,0:56:25.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有澄海\N{\rOriginal text}You got the Sea of Serenity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.69,0:56:28.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}危海 我們很快便排除了這個\N{\rOriginal text}Sea of Crises. We crossed that one off the list pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.82,0:56:30.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 這個名字不利於宣傳\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. That's bad PR.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.53,0:56:34.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們最後決定在寧靜海著陸\N{\rOriginal text}And then we finally settled on, uh, the Sea of Tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.66,0:56:36.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是最佳地點\N{\rOriginal text}That's the sweet spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.33,0:56:42.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這麼一想 我... 對月球的瞭解\N{\rOriginal text}You know, come to think about it, I... I know a lot more about the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.75,0:56:45.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}遠遠超過我對你的瞭解\N{\rOriginal text}than I know about you by a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.71,0:56:48.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我甚至不知道你是哪裏人\N{\rOriginal text}I don't even know where you're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.63,0:56:51.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}堪薩斯\N{\rOriginal text}Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.18,0:56:55.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}來自堪薩斯的凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly from Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.31,0:56:58.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}堪薩斯的凱莉 你是怎麼進入廣告這一行的?\N{\rOriginal text}How'd you get into advertising, Kelly from Kansas?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.10,0:57:06.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我爸爸離開時我四歲 媽媽失去了房子\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, well, I was four when my dad left, and my mom lost the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.27,0:57:07.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們住在汽車裏\N{\rOriginal text}We lived in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.11,0:57:12.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一個教堂給了她一份賣曲奇罐的工作\N{\rOriginal text}And... a church gave her a job selling cookie tins.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.91,0:57:19.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以她想了個點子 如果由我挨家挨戶推銷就能賣出更多\N{\rOriginal text}So, she had this idea that we'd sell more if it was me going door-to-door.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.08,0:57:21.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是啊 聰明的女士\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, yeah. Smart lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.25,0:57:27.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}曲奇罐 然後賣吸塵器 我長大些就轉而賣美容用品\N{\rOriginal text}Cookie tins, then it was vacuums, then beauty goods when I got older.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.71,0:57:30.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的 我和我媽周遊全國\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. Traveling the country, me and my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.88,0:57:33.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們的生活就是這樣重回正軌的\N{\rOriginal text}It's how we got back on our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.01,0:57:37.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很遺憾你不得不經歷這些\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I'm sorry you went through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.35,0:57:43.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不必 我...\N{\rOriginal text}Well, don't be. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.52,0:57:47.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 我很小就學會了如何生存\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. I learned early on how to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.94,0:57:54.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而且家家都有本難念的經\N{\rOriginal text}Plus, we all have our share of tough breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.08,0:58:01.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利跟我說了 心房顫動和你被計劃除名的事\N{\rOriginal text}Henry told me about the A-fib and you getting kicked out of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.08,0:58:05.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我得去跟亨利聊聊\N{\rOriginal text}Hmm. I'm gonna have to have a little conversation with Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.13,0:58:12.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不過我並不完全贊同你的說法\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I don't totally agree with you though.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.72,0:58:18.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼講? 我就是不...\N{\rOriginal text}How's that? Well, I just don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.18,0:58:22.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不認為我們的悲傷故事\N{\rOriginal text}I don't think that our sad stories are supposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.23,0:58:23.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就該教會我們如何在世上生存\N{\rOriginal text}teach us how to survive the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.52,0:58:27.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我認為它們應該激勵我們去改變世界\N{\rOriginal text}I think they're supposed to make us wanna change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.65,0:58:31.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科爾\N{\rOriginal text}Hmm. Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.73,0:58:34.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}巴茲正在試圖短路發動你的科邁羅\N{\rOriginal text}Buzz is trying to hot-wire your Camaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.15,0:58:36.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜託 天啊\N{\rOriginal text}Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.82,0:58:38.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那麼...\N{\rOriginal text}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.91,0:58:41.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你最好去阻止他\N{\rOriginal text}You better go stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.25,0:58:44.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.60,0:59:02.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(衛星汽車旅館)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.23,0:59:09.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}老天\N{\rOriginal text}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.56,0:59:11.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們得談談\N{\rOriginal text}We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.19,0:59:18.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿凱 你的工作做得十分出色\N{\rOriginal text}You have done outstanding work, Kel.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.70,0:59:20.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}公眾的興趣大大提高了\N{\rOriginal text}Public interest is way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.33,0:59:25.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你搞定了參議員們 確保發射能順利進行\N{\rOriginal text}You landed the senators and secured the launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.96,0:59:28.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所以你就闖進我的旅店房間?\N{\rOriginal text}And that's why you broke into my motel room?
