Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.56,1:01:10.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}同樣 科爾·戴維斯也會永遠蒙在鼓裏\N{\rOriginal text}in the same way that Cole Davis will never know about it.
