Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.22,1:01:54.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 你手裏最厲害 但卻沒人聽說過的導演是誰?\N{\rOriginal text}Now, who's the best director you've got that no one's ever heard of?
