Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.61,1:02:04.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是基地裏最偏遠的飛機庫\N{\rOriginal text}This is the most remote hangar on the base.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.57,1:02:07.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有我的允許 任何人不得出入\N{\rOriginal text}No one can go in or out without my permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.74,1:02:09.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 任何人? 連科爾都不行?\N{\rOriginal text}Wait, no one? Not even Cole?
