Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.62,1:05:04.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們需要細節 具體細節\N{\rOriginal text}We need details. Specifics.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.71,1:05:08.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是多塵 多石還是有風? 光源是怎樣的?\N{\rOriginal text}Is it dusty, rocky, windy? What is the light source? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.34,1:05:12.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就是太陽咯 大燈 別自作聰明 愛德華\N{\rOriginal text}It's the sun. Big light. Do not smart-mouth me, Edvard.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.30,1:05:16.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太陽和著陸區的位置關係是怎樣的?\N{\rOriginal text}And what is the sun's position in relation to the landing area?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.10,1:05:18.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們要建一個仿製版嗎? 我們有計劃嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}And are we building a replica? Do we have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.18,1:05:21.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們有宇航服嗎? 演員穿上宇航服如何行動?\N{\rOriginal text}Do we have suits, and how do people move in those suits?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.73,1:05:24.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還有 凱莉 太空裏到底什麼樣子?\N{\rOriginal text}And what, Kelly, does space even look like?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.27,1:05:26.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 得躺一下\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I gotta... I gotta lie down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.27,1:05:28.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的拖車呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Where is my trailer?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.32,1:05:34.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們得想辦法 把那個模擬室裏的一切都照搬過來\N{\rOriginal text}We need to find a way to copy everything in that simulation room.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.70,1:05:36.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好的 盡快\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.33,1:05:38.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 我有拖車嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Wait a second. Do I even have a trailer?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.58,1:05:41.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不說話我也知道\N{\rOriginal text}Your silence tells me what I already know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.54,1:05:43.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你還沒想過怎樣復刻月球\N{\rOriginal text}You haven't thought about how to recreate the moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.58,1:05:46.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼會想拖車的事? 我覺得我們該找庫布裏克了\N{\rOriginal text}why would you think about a trailer? I think we should've gotten Kubrick.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.63,1:05:48.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們必須把新的飛船做對了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got to get this new ship right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.50,1:05:50.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗很生氣\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, Armstrong, he was pissed off
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.26,1:05:51.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們不能再惹他了 抱歉\N{\rOriginal text}and we can't have that again. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.38,1:05:54.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}夥計...\N{\rOriginal text}Buddy, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.43,1:05:56.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等... 這些都是敏感材料\N{\rOriginal text}Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa. This is sensitive material.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.47,1:05:58.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}亨利... 不行 你不能待在這裏\N{\rOriginal text}Henry. Henry. Uh-uh. You can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.39,1:06:01.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這些照片是為了企鵝出版社的檔案書拍的\N{\rOriginal text}These photos are for the archival book that Penguin is doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.18,1:06:02.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什麼書? 對 你沒收到備忘錄?\N{\rOriginal text}What book? Yeah, didn't you get the memo?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.98,1:06:04.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有 什麼? 你要寫前言\N{\rOriginal text}No. What? You're writing the foreword.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.44,1:06:07.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 寫前言? 對 是啊\N{\rOriginal text}I... I'm writing the foreword? Yeah, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.27,1:06:08.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我? 沒錯\N{\rOriginal text}Me? Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.82,1:06:11.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我從沒寫過前言 編輯想聽聽你的話\N{\rOriginal text}I've never written a foreword. The editor wants to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.19,1:06:12.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們都想 他要我寫?\N{\rOriginal text}We all do. He wants me to write it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.49,1:06:14.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別這麼謙虛好嗎? 我們給你拍一張和...\N{\rOriginal text}Don't be so humble, all right? Let's get a photo of you with the...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.82,1:06:16.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月艙的合影 我可以寫 但...\N{\rOriginal text}with the LEM. I mean, I can do it, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.41,1:06:17.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}說「我們要登月了」\N{\rOriginal text}Say, "we're going to the moon."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.62,1:06:19.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們要登月了 真不錯\N{\rOriginal text}We're going to the moon. There you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.29,1:06:23.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}奧爾德林和阿姆斯特朗 每一個動作都要練習\N{\rOriginal text}Aldrin and Armstrong will practice every single movement that they make,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.46,1:06:25.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在這裏練好幾個月\N{\rOriginal text}um, right here for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.33,1:06:26.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真了不起 是\N{\rOriginal text}That is incredible. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.71,1:06:28.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這就是月球表面?\N{\rOriginal text}So, this is, like, the surface of the moon?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.96,1:06:30.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是 這... 對\N{\rOriginal text}Well, yeah. It's... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.09,1:06:31.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是我們最接近的模擬\N{\rOriginal text}It's our best approximation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.97,1:06:34.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這看起來就像個骯髒的海灘 我不信 不可能\N{\rOriginal text}This just looks like a dirty beach. I don't believe it. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.38,1:06:36.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是按... 我們得到的沉積物做的 約瑟夫\N{\rOriginal text}It is... It's based off sediment we got. Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.34,1:06:37.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}來自航天局\N{\rOriginal text}It's from NASA...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.26,1:06:40.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 我不相信這就是國家航空航天局\N{\rOriginal text}Wait. I do not believe this is what NASA uses
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.14,1:06:42.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}用來登月的裝備 你別告訴我... 不行\N{\rOriginal text}to go to the moon. You cannot tell me... No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.31,1:06:46.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要你們假裝抱著母親在沙漠裏行走\N{\rOriginal text}Want you to walk as if you're carrying your mother across the desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.40,1:06:49.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她很脆弱 但也很重\N{\rOriginal text}She's frail but also heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.61,1:06:51.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 嘿\N{\rOriginal text}Oh. Whoa. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.28,1:06:52.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真抱歉 嘿 對不起 不能拍...\N{\rOriginal text}So sorry. Hey. Sorry. Oh, no, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.82,1:06:54.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是機密 你不能... 斯圖 沒事\N{\rOriginal text}This is classified. You're not allow... Stu, we're good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.61,1:06:56.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是機密 沒事 這是為那本書拍的\N{\rOriginal text}Very classified. We're good here. This is for the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.45,1:06:57.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你會聽說的\N{\rOriginal text}No, you'll hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.57,1:06:58.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要寫前言\N{\rOriginal text}I'm doing the foreword,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.49,1:06:59.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你很快會聽說的 好吧\N{\rOriginal text}so you'll hear about it soon. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.83,1:07:02.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我這個阿姆斯特朗是個總愛抱怨的爛人 我們得重新選角\N{\rOriginal text}My Armstrong is a whiny, little bitch. We have to recast.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.66,1:07:04.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 我們不重新選角\N{\rOriginal text}No... We're not recasting.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.83,1:07:06.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 那就平庸著拍吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Well, mediocre it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.54,1:07:09.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}愛德華 我的太陽呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Edvard! Where is my sun?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.84,1:07:10.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好\N{\rOriginal text}Nice!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.84,1:07:12.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常好 至少來個倒數啊\N{\rOriginal text}Very nice. A countdown at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.09,1:07:14.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 再開一次\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Try it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.34,1:07:15.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我再開一次 從三倒數\N{\rOriginal text}Gonna try it again. Do a three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.97,1:07:17.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜託 滿意嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Come on! Ah! Happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.05,1:07:19.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}約瑟夫 給我拿汽水來\N{\rOriginal text}J... Joseph, bring me my Tab.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.35,1:07:21.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你得來找我 因為我眼都瞎了\N{\rOriginal text}You're gonna have to find me 'cause I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.60,1:07:23.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜託 拿個汽水要多久?\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. How long does it take to give someone a Tab?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.73,1:07:25.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的手就在這裏\N{\rOriginal text}My hand's right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.31,1:07:27.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一定會很棒的 你們都該聚過來\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, this will be great. You guys should all come around
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.31,1:07:29.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們來給那本書拍一張 很好吧?\N{\rOriginal text}and we'll do a shot for the book. Great?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.48,1:07:32.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 各位 這麼說如何? 「我們要登月了」\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, how about this? Everybody, "We're going to the moon!"
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.03,1:07:35.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們要登月了\N{\rOriginal text}We're going to the moon!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.90,1:07:38.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我好像眨眼了 再拍一張?\N{\rOriginal text}My eyes might have been closed. You wanna do one more?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.70,1:07:43.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最近沒看到你\N{\rOriginal text}I haven't seen you around lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.33,1:07:45.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}彼此彼此\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I can say the same thing about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.33,1:07:49.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎麼一次就繫好了?\N{\rOriginal text}How do you do it on the first try?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.04,1:07:52.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這又不是多複雜的事 好 準備好了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}It's not rocket science. Okay. You good?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.55,1:07:54.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那些問題 我... 是的\N{\rOriginal text}About the questions, I... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.76,1:07:59.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我都看過了 沒有關於阿波羅1號的 他們答應過我 好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}I went over them. Nothing about Apollo 1. They promised me. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.51,1:08:02.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你會表現得很好的 明白嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You're gonna be great. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.26,1:08:03.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}去吧\N{\rOriginal text}Mm-hmm. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.51,1:08:04.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 上\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.19,1:08:10.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴維斯先生 你是我們口中的「採訪困難戶」\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis. You are what we call "a tough get."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.10,1:08:11.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哪有 謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}Ha! No. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.19,1:08:14.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們將看到尼爾阿姆斯特朗 和巴茲奧爾德林走上月球表面\N{\rOriginal text}Is there any legal importance to what we'll be watching
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.48,1:08:18.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這有什麼法律方面的重要意義嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}when Neil Armstrong and Buzz Aldrin walk on the lunar surface?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.11,1:08:22.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們著陸的區域會被視為歸美國所有嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Will the area they land on be considered property of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.16,1:08:25.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們要送一塊匾上去 寫著「我們為全人類的和平而來」\N{\rOriginal text}We're sending a plaque that says, "We came in peace for all mankind."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.83,1:08:27.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那正是我們的意思\N{\rOriginal text}And that is precisely what we mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.41,1:08:29.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}國家航空航天局還會留下其他什麼東西?\N{\rOriginal text}What else will NASA leave behind?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.96,1:08:32.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}足跡 一面美國國旗和12袋糞便\N{\rOriginal text}Footprints, an American flag and 12 bags of feces
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.29,1:08:35.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們跟我說了很多次不要提 但是...\N{\rOriginal text}that I was told many times that I should not bring up, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.25,1:08:37.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們真該早點讓他接受採訪\N{\rOriginal text}Should've put him in front of a camera sooner.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.22,1:08:38.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你戴著一枚阿波羅胸針\N{\rOriginal text}You wear an Apollo pin.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.93,1:08:41.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}I do. Um,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.43,1:08:43.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是阿波羅1號乘組的太太們\N{\rOriginal text}the wives of Apollo 1's men,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.01,1:08:47.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在丈夫們犧牲後送我的\N{\rOriginal text}after we lost them, they gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.10,1:08:50.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在那悲劇的一天 你是發射主管\N{\rOriginal text}You were launch director on that tragic day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.02,1:08:53.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅1號出了什麼故障?\N{\rOriginal text}What went wrong with Apollo 1?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.99,1:08:59.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}用你自己的話說 發生了什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}In your own words, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.49,1:09:02.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幫我回顧一下\N{\rOriginal text}Take me back.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.79,1:09:09.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我來給你列舉一些事實\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Here's some facts for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.83,1:09:11.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}《紐約時報》報道\N{\rOriginal text}The New York Times reported
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.00,1:09:13.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那艘飛船曾有兩萬份安全事件報告\N{\rOriginal text}there were 20,000 safety reports filed about that ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.71,1:09:17.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}實在太多 以至於加斯·格裏森 用一個檸檬表示自己的不滿\N{\rOriginal text}So many, that Gus Grissom hung a lemon outside it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.97,1:09:22.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 乘組 待確認 位置\N{\rOriginal text}All right, crew. To be confirmed. Location.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.97,1:09:23.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}著火了\N{\rOriginal text}Flame!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.97,1:09:26.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}駕駛艙裏失火了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got a fire in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.06,1:09:26.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快出去\N{\rOriginal text}Let's get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.97,1:09:29.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴維斯先生 你讀過那些報告嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis? Did you read those reports?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.98,1:09:32.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射台主管 快進去救他們\N{\rOriginal text}Pad leader, get in there and help 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.65,1:09:34.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射台主管 盯著C3\N{\rOriginal text}Pad leader, stay on C3.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.61,1:09:43.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}戴維斯先生 你讀過那些報告嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Mr. Davis? Did you read those reports?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.32,1:09:49.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你讀過那些報告嗎? 我當然讀過那些報告\N{\rOriginal text}Did you read those reports? Of course I read the reports.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.95,1:09:51.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每一份都讀過\N{\rOriginal text}I read every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.16,1:09:55.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}獨立供電測試期間 氧氣壓力過高的同時遇到了線路故障\N{\rOriginal text}Overpressured oxygen and a bad wire on a "plugs-out" test.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.17,1:10:00.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我本該查出一切問題的 我看漏了 辜負了他們\N{\rOriginal text}I was supposed to catch everything, and I missed it. And I failed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.21,1:10:03.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我餘生中的每一天都會為此感到愧疚\N{\rOriginal text}And I will live with that every single day for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.05,1:10:05.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人渣 這是你想引述的原話嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Is that the quote that you were looking for, you piece of shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.68,1:10:08.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讓我跟你的老闆通話 立刻 馬上\N{\rOriginal text}Get me on the phone with your boss. Now. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.39,1:10:12.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 你幹什麼? 採訪還有20分鐘\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, uh, wait. W-What are you doing? We have another 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.39,1:10:13.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}去死吧\N{\rOriginal text}Go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.48,1:10:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別生我的氣 害死三個宇航員的人不是我\N{\rOriginal text}Don't be angry with me. I'm not the reason three astronauts are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.90,1:10:22.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你再提一句那些宇航員試試 嘿... 別衝動\N{\rOriginal text}Say one more thing about the astronauts. Hey, hey, hey! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.99,1:10:24.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}放開我 你再說一句試試\N{\rOriginal text}Get off me. Let me hear you say one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.91,1:10:26.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你再提他們一句試試\N{\rOriginal text}Let me hear you say one more thing about them!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.70,1:10:28.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你不認識他們 你不准再提他們\N{\rOriginal text}You don't know those men! You don't talk about those men!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.87,1:10:30.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}放開我 放開\N{\rOriginal text}Get off me! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.66,1:10:31.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}放開\N{\rOriginal text}Get off!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.25,1:10:33.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽懂了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.30,1:10:43.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟製作人們談過了 他們同意不播出這段採訪\N{\rOriginal text}So, I spoke to the producers, and they've agreed to seal the film
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.47,1:10:47.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}條件是阿姆斯特朗著陸後 給他們獨家採訪\N{\rOriginal text}if we give them the exclusive with Armstrong after he lands.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.35,1:10:54.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不過我們失去了赫奇斯的支持 他要投反對票了\N{\rOriginal text}We lost Hedges though. He's voting no.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.48,1:10:59.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你說過他們不會問的 是的 他們撒謊了\N{\rOriginal text}You said they wouldn't ask about it. Yeah. Well... they lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.94,1:11:01.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人們有時是會撒謊的 科爾\N{\rOriginal text}You know, people do that sometimes, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.57,1:11:03.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你也許可以說點假話 那也算為自己\N{\rOriginal text}You could have done yourself and this program a favor
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.57,1:11:05.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}和這登月計劃幫了個忙 對嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}and maybe tried it yourself. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.61,1:11:07.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}責怪國家航空航天局\N{\rOriginal text}Blame NASA.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.45,1:11:08.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}責怪這個體系\N{\rOriginal text}Blame the system.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.45,1:11:12.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}事關價值五億美元的資金啊\N{\rOriginal text}I mean, there was half a billion dollars worth of funding on the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.12,1:11:14.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}撒謊對你來說一定輕而易舉吧 畢竟你總在撒謊\N{\rOriginal text}Lying must be so easy for you when you do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.46,1:11:15.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}撒謊總是一個可選項\N{\rOriginal text}It's just always an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.67,1:11:18.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你該試試說真話 你裝什麼清高呢?\N{\rOriginal text}What you should try is the truth. What is this sanctimonious bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.21,1:11:20.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我永遠不會就那些人或那一天的事撒謊\N{\rOriginal text}I'm never going to lie about those men or that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.88,1:11:22.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你明白嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.96,1:11:24.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}隨便你怎麼看我\N{\rOriginal text}You think what you want about me,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.63,1:11:28.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但因為不冷靜 而讓全人類登月夢破碎的人不是我\N{\rOriginal text}but I didn't cost the world a dream because I lost my goddamn cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.33,1:12:02.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是34號發射場 發生阿波羅1號悲劇的地方\N{\rOriginal text}This is Launch Complex 34, where the Apollo 1 tragedy occurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.50,1:12:05.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是犧牲英雄的紀念碑\N{\rOriginal text}This is a tribute to our fallen heroes,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.21,1:12:08.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這些勇敢的人為我們的成功鋪平了道路\N{\rOriginal text}the brave men who paved the road to our success.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.84,1:12:12.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請大家為他們默哀片刻\N{\rOriginal text}Please, let's take a moment of silence for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.86,1:12:25.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}愛德華 真令人稱奇\N{\rOriginal text}Edvard, that looks incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.19,1:12:27.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我完全看不到線纜 你怎麼做到的?\N{\rOriginal text}I can't see the wires at all. How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.03,1:12:29.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只是用了一塊遮光板 很簡單\N{\rOriginal text}I just put a flag. It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.03,1:12:29.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}老辦法了\N{\rOriginal text}Old school. Huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.95,1:12:32.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行 從頭再來\N{\rOriginal text}No. Again. From the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.45,1:12:35.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這次多加一些跳躍\N{\rOriginal text}And maybe let's get some more bounce this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.12,1:12:36.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們可是在月球上啊\N{\rOriginal text}You are on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.75,1:12:38.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.42,1:12:46.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 我看不下去了 今天不行\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my God. I-I can't. I can't with this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.88,1:12:50.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 好 堅持住 約瑟夫 失火了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, dear. Uh... Okay, hold on. Joseph, there's a fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.80,1:12:51.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我來\N{\rOriginal text}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.60,1:12:54.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別忘記四步口訣\N{\rOriginal text}Don't forget to PASS.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.90,1:13:03.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 能放他們下來嗎? 算了 掛著吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Can you bring them down? Actually, leave them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.23,1:13:05.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讓他們反思一下自己都幹了什麼\N{\rOriginal text}Let them think about what they did.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.32,1:13:09.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我放棄了 我去吃午飯\N{\rOriginal text}I give up. I'm taking lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.24,1:13:16.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們明白自己幹了什麼嗎? 你們讓她提早去吃午飯了\N{\rOriginal text}You see what you did? You made her take lunch early.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.37,1:13:18.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這都怪你們\N{\rOriginal text}That's on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.01,1:13:32.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我跟你賭5美元 你不擅長道歉\N{\rOriginal text}I'll bet you $5 you're bad at apologies.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.47,1:13:33.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我到處找你\N{\rOriginal text}I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.76,1:13:35.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你欠我5塊 我有個想法\N{\rOriginal text}You owe me five bucks. I got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.35,1:13:36.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.43,1:13:38.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}來 去路易斯安那州的路上告訴你\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. I'll tell you on the way to Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.89,1:13:41.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 你想嘗試獲得范寧的投票?\N{\rOriginal text}No. You wanna take a shot at Vanning?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.98,1:13:44.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我給咱們弄到了晚餐邀請 就是今晚 走吧\N{\rOriginal text}I got us a dinner invite, for tonight. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.94,1:13:46.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今晚? 我們不可能趕得上 有800公里呢\N{\rOriginal text}Tonight? We're never gonna make it. It's 500 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.98,1:13:49.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們能趕上 來 你得相信我\N{\rOriginal text}We're gonna make it. Come on. You gotta trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.94,1:13:50.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 不\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, wait. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.99,1:13:52.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行... 什麼叫「不行」?\N{\rOriginal text}No, no, no. What do you mean, "no"?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.32,1:13:54.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們不能... 有其他... 我們可以... 你想不想要范寧支持?\N{\rOriginal text}We don't... There's other... We could... Do you want Vanning or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.70,1:13:56.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不... 來 我們走\N{\rOriginal text}Ugh. No. I don't... Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.66,1:13:58.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我覺得我們可以乘民航 如果我們出發...\N{\rOriginal text}I think we could just take a commercial flight. If we left...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.83,1:14:00.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行 現在沒有民航航班\N{\rOriginal text}Nope. No commercial flights are flying right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.75,1:14:02.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}來 跳上來\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. Just hop on in.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.42,1:14:05.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就是這樣 你只管上來就行 你可以跳上來的 你行的\N{\rOriginal text}This is it. This is all you gotta do. You can hop up, you can get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.13,1:14:06.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}腳踩那裏 好吧 拿著我的鞋\N{\rOriginal text}Put your foot there. Okay, well, take these.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.92,1:14:08.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}聽著 我們得走了 好\N{\rOriginal text}Look, we gotta go. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.38,1:14:09.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等...\N{\rOriginal text}Hold on. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.13,1:14:13.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}完美\N{\rOriginal text}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.26,1:14:15.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}等等 沒問題\N{\rOriginal text}Hold on. We're good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.90,1:14:27.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}風景不錯吧?\N{\rOriginal text}You enjoying the view?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.27,1:14:28.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 太美了\N{\rOriginal text}Wow! It's stunning!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.61,1:14:31.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我打賭你閉著眼呢\N{\rOriginal text}I bet your eyes are closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.24,1:14:33.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有\N{\rOriginal text}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.17,1:14:46.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我猜你還會些其他南方口音\N{\rOriginal text}So, I'm betting you have some other Southern accents
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.96,1:14:48.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}畢竟你「多才多藝」 會路易斯安那的嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}in that bag of tricks of yours. Can you do Louisiana?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.92,1:14:50.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}會 新奧爾良還是巴吞魯日?\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah. New Orleans or Baton Rouge?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.46,1:14:52.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}用他老婆家鄉的 好\N{\rOriginal text}Wherever his wife's from. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.68,1:14:56.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科爾·戴維斯\N{\rOriginal text}Cole Davis.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.01,1:14:57.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你一定是凱莉·瓊斯小姐\N{\rOriginal text}And you must be Miss Kelly Jones.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.89,1:14:59.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兩位請進\N{\rOriginal text}Please come in, y'all. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.31,1:15:00.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常感謝你們邀請我們吃晚餐\N{\rOriginal text}Thank you so much for having us for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.89,1:15:04.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好... 我聽說你是紐約城裏人\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, now... now, I was told you were a New York City type.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.48,1:15:06.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 不是 我只是在那裏工作 我是路易斯安那人\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, God, no. I just work there. I'm from Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.94,1:15:08.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}土生土長的 也會落葉歸根\N{\rOriginal text}Born and raised and, one day, buried.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.31,1:15:11.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我老家在弗吉尼亞 不會吧? 我們是親人啊\N{\rOriginal text}I'm from Virginia. No? We're family.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.07,1:15:14.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}特克·斯裏特爾總說 弗吉尼亞是得克薩斯的母親\N{\rOriginal text}You know, Tex Ritter always said Virginia was the mother of Texas.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.65,1:15:17.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們一直不知道父親是誰 總懷疑是路易斯安那\N{\rOriginal text}Well, we never knew who the father was. We always suspected it was Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.91,1:15:19.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我媽可喜歡這個笑話了\N{\rOriginal text}Oh! Huh? My mother loves that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.91,1:15:22.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是她想出來的 太有意思了\N{\rOriginal text}She was the one that came up with it. Oh, just so colorful.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.08,1:15:25.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你真有趣 你家可真漂亮\N{\rOriginal text}You're fun. This is a beautiful home.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.33,1:15:31.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}參議員 競選活動怎麼樣?\N{\rOriginal text}So, h-how is the campaign going, Senator?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.71,1:15:35.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}說實話 政治更像是我的一項愛好\N{\rOriginal text}Truth be told, politics is more of a hobby to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.09,1:15:40.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}服事基督才是我的全職工作\N{\rOriginal text}Serving Christ, that's my full-time job.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.93,1:15:44.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}現在美國正有一場針對宗教的戰爭\N{\rOriginal text}You know, there's a war on religion in this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.48,1:15:47.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}有人說要怪科學\N{\rOriginal text}And some say science is to blame.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.44,1:15:50.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是科學讓我們今天齊聚一堂\N{\rOriginal text}Well, science is what brought us to this table.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.57,1:15:53.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你從阿波羅1號的事上學到了\N{\rOriginal text}You learned a little lesson on the provocation of pride
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.19,1:15:55.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}關於驕傲的一課 科爾 不是嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}on Apollo 1, now, didn't you, Cole?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.95,1:16:01.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其實科學讓我離上帝更近了 先生\N{\rOriginal text}Science has actually brought me closer to God, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.66,1:16:05.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}上帝用了六天創造了我們所知的一切\N{\rOriginal text}Took the Lord six days to put forth everything that we know as creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.54,1:16:07.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}第六天 他把這些交給我們管理\N{\rOriginal text}And on that sixth day he gave us dominion over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.92,1:16:10.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我個人認為這是一種責任\N{\rOriginal text}And, personally, I take that as a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.46,1:16:15.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你聽起來很虔誠\N{\rOriginal text}You sound like a man who knows his way to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.42,1:16:18.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我覺得最能體現虔誠的方法\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I can't think of a greater act of faith
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.84,1:16:20.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫過於追逐星辰\N{\rOriginal text}than pursuing the stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.51,1:16:25.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「諸天述說上帝的榮耀 穹蒼傳揚他的作為」\N{\rOriginal text}"The heavens declare the glory of God. And the firmament shows us his handiwork."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.52,1:16:29.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是喬琳娜最喜歡的詩篇句子之一\N{\rOriginal text}That's one of Jolene's favorite Psalms.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.15,1:16:31.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是這樣 等我們的人從太空歸來\N{\rOriginal text}You see, our men, when they come back from space,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.69,1:16:34.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們對上帝的信仰會更多 不會減少\N{\rOriginal text}they believe more in God, not less.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.49,1:16:37.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我們登月時\N{\rOriginal text}But when we land on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.49,1:16:43.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}多虧了這位瓊斯小姐 全球都能看到\N{\rOriginal text}and thanks to Miss Jones here, the world watches us do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.16,1:16:47.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我希望世界各地的人都能感受到 那種聖神的存在\N{\rOriginal text}And it's my hope that people everywhere feel the presence of that divine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.83,1:16:52.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧\N{\rOriginal text}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.63,1:16:58.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的話確實得讓我好好想想 小伙子\N{\rOriginal text}you've, uh, certainly given me a lot to think about, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.64,1:17:09.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你這推銷還真有說服力啊\N{\rOriginal text}You really sold the hell out of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.85,1:17:11.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我沒在推銷\N{\rOriginal text}I wasn't selling.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.98,1:17:16.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}鄭重聲明 做真實的自己也能贏得人心\N{\rOriginal text}For the record, you can win people over just by being who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.86,1:17:24.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們現在不趕時間了 所以不必飛回去\N{\rOriginal text}You know, we're not in a rush, so we don't really have to fly home.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.87,1:17:26.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那可不算飛\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh. That wasn't flying.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.09,1:17:39.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜託 睜開眼睛\N{\rOriginal text}Come on. Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.48,1:17:51.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}相信我嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You trust me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.90,1:17:55.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}坐穩了\N{\rOriginal text}Hold tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.70,1:18:07.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}現在才是最好玩的 滑下來就行\N{\rOriginal text}Now, this is the fun part. Just slide off.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.37,1:18:13.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}完美\N{\rOriginal text}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.75,1:19:05.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我過去對國家航空航天局的計劃 有過諸多意見不一致的地方\N{\rOriginal text}I've had my disagreements with the NASA program in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.43,1:19:09.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但經過深思熟慮和反覆祈禱後\N{\rOriginal text}But after a great deal of thought, and prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.97,1:19:12.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我決定投贊成票\N{\rOriginal text}I've decided to vote yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.48,1:19:17.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好樣的\N{\rOriginal text}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.11,1:19:21.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有樣東西 你一定得看看\N{\rOriginal text}I have something that you need to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.49,1:19:23.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}什麼... 跟我來\N{\rOriginal text}What... Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.57,1:19:25.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我之前不知道結果會如何\N{\rOriginal text}Whoo! I didn't know which way it was gonna go,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.91,1:19:28.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為你根本看不透政客\N{\rOriginal text}'cause you can't tell with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.12,1:19:31.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我之前向來不喜歡這傢伙\N{\rOriginal text}I never liked that guy before, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.08,1:19:33.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我現在喜歡他了\N{\rOriginal text}I like him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.71,1:19:34.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太好了\N{\rOriginal text}All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.96,1:19:37.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏好黑啊 你... 快到了\N{\rOriginal text}It's so dark in here. You... Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.13,1:19:39.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我有點害怕 好了 就在這裏\N{\rOriginal text}I'm a little scared. Yeah, it's right around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.84,1:19:41.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(對你的感謝有如登月往返)
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.71,1:19:44.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們想對你表達謝意\N{\rOriginal text}We wanted to show you our appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.51,1:19:47.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 這也太隆重了 謝謝\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my gosh. This is too much. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.89,1:19:49.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不敢相信 都是沃爾特的功勞\N{\rOriginal text}I can't believe it. It was all Walter.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.93,1:19:51.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沃爾特? 我知道這都是你操辦的 對吧?\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, Walter? I know that you did all of this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.97,1:19:53.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}出了點力而已 是 我知道是你\N{\rOriginal text}A little. That's all. Yeah, I know you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.89,1:19:55.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大家都幫忙了 還不錯吧?\N{\rOriginal text}They all helped. Not too bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.49,1:20:13.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}趁我還沒忘 給\N{\rOriginal text}Before I forget. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.95,1:20:16.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這上面列出了 登月後你邁出第一步時可以說的話\N{\rOriginal text}It's a list of things for you to say when you take your first step.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.50,1:20:19.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 知道所有人都在問你 就是想給你些點子\N{\rOriginal text}I... I know everybody's asking you. I thought I'd give you some options.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.25,1:20:21.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我本來想說\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I was just gonna say,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.59,1:20:23.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「看這些酷酷的石頭」之類的話\N{\rOriginal text}"Look at all those cool rocks," or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.96,1:20:26.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我能搞定的 凱莉 好\N{\rOriginal text}I got this one, Kelly. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.34,1:20:28.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不過謝謝你\N{\rOriginal text}And thank you, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.55,1:20:32.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真心的 謝謝... 你所做的一切\N{\rOriginal text}And I mean it. For, uh... For everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.14,1:20:38.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我覺得沒有人比科爾·戴維斯 更在乎這個計劃\N{\rOriginal text}You know, I don't think anyone cares about this program more than Cole Davis.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.77,1:20:43.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很高興看見他有其他在乎的東西了\N{\rOriginal text}It's nice to see he's found something else to care about.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.63,1:21:06.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道我不是宇航員 但我能請你跳一支舞嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}I know I'm no, uh, astronaut, but can I steal you for a dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.55,1:21:09.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可以 可以? 來\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. Yes. Yeah? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.64,1:21:22.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你在數著日子 等待回到曼哈頓的那一天嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}So, you just counting down the days until you, uh, can get back to Manhattan?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.69,1:21:23.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}並沒有\N{\rOriginal text}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.98,1:21:25.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好\N{\rOriginal text}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.00,1:21:48.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}往上... 很好 好了 把燈搬過來\N{\rOriginal text}Up, up, up. Perfect. Right, now, move the light in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.30,1:21:50.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 繼續 別害羞\N{\rOriginal text}All right, keep going. Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.34,1:21:53.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}繼續...\N{\rOriginal text}Keep going. Keep going. Keep going. Keep going. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.89,1:21:57.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}充分利用 很好\N{\rOriginal text}Milk it. Good. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.68,1:22:00.93,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}女士們 覺得如何?\N{\rOriginal text}Ladies, what do we think?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.94,1:22:03.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}蘭斯 太驚人了 很棒\N{\rOriginal text}Lance, it's incredible. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.40,1:22:07.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我覺得還需要再來點塵土和更好的演員\N{\rOriginal text}I think it needs a little more dust and better actors,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.28,1:22:09.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但我的要求被拒了\N{\rOriginal text}but I lost that battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.94,1:22:10.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我也就不糾結了\N{\rOriginal text}I will let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.03,1:22:14.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}停 好\N{\rOriginal text}And, stop. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.99,1:22:16.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們有太陽了\N{\rOriginal text}We've got our sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.91,1:22:19.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我總是配合你編造的那些謊言\N{\rOriginal text}I always went along with every web you spun
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.04,1:22:23.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}要麼是因為它們很有趣 要麼我們是在騙壞人\N{\rOriginal text}because it was fun or, like, we were pulling one over on the bad guys,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.08,1:22:25.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但這次的感覺...\N{\rOriginal text}but this feels...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.13,1:22:26.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道\N{\rOriginal text}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.00,1:22:29.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就快完工了\N{\rOriginal text}We're almost done.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.47,1:22:35.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是我送你的\N{\rOriginal text}This is from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.76,1:22:37.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射日禮物\N{\rOriginal text}It is for launch day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.01,1:22:40.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}答應我 到時候再拆\N{\rOriginal text}Promise you will wait until then.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.73,1:22:42.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我答應 好\N{\rOriginal text}I promise. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.77,1:22:46.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}記住 你們不是怪獸\N{\rOriginal text}Remember, you're not monsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.19,1:22:49.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}會跳那麼高嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Are they gonna be that high?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.44,1:22:52.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只需要讓他們的跳躍距離\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, I just need to give them any length
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.70,1:22:55.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}看起來像在月球上即可 但謝謝你的意見\N{\rOriginal text}that looks like they're on the moon. But thank you for the note.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.70,1:22:57.20,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}巴茲 動作幅度小一點\N{\rOriginal text}Buzz, take it down some.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.83,1:22:59.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗 不要看我尋求肯定\N{\rOriginal text}And, Armstrong, stop looking at me for approval.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.99,1:23:03.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}專心演好身處月球 把我當空氣 他排練得很開心...\N{\rOriginal text}Just be on the moon. I'm not here. He's having fun. He's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.67,1:23:06.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他總是和我四目相交 別暗送秋波了 專心演身處月球\N{\rOriginal text}He keeps locking eyes with me. Stop flirting and be on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.80,1:23:18.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}昨天的科幻小說成為了今天的現實\N{\rOriginal text}Yesterday's science fiction is today's fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.85,1:23:20.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}方法雖然不同\N{\rOriginal text}The methods are different,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.26,1:23:22.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但重要的是明天一早\N{\rOriginal text}but the important thing is that tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.81,1:23:25.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}人類將飛向月球\N{\rOriginal text}man will lift off toward the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.82,1:23:40.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}晚上好 我是沃爾特·克朗凱特\N{\rOriginal text}Good evening. I'm Walter Cronkite.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.24,1:23:44.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在人類首次登月之旅的前夕\N{\rOriginal text}And on this eve of man's first flight toward a landing on the moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.25,1:23:46.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有的準備工作都很順利\N{\rOriginal text}all preparations go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.79,1:23:48.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天氣預報狀況良好\N{\rOriginal text}The weather prediction,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.21,1:23:51.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}還有宇航員們的幫助 尼爾 阿姆...\N{\rOriginal text}along with the health of astronauts, Neil Arm...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.20,1:24:21.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼了?\N{\rOriginal text}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.75,1:24:34.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你很會傷人心啊\N{\rOriginal text}Well, you know how to hurt a fella.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.21,1:24:36.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}禮貌性的電話都不打一個?\N{\rOriginal text}No courtesy call?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.55,1:24:38.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我沒有你的電話號碼\N{\rOriginal text}Well, I don't have your number.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.26,1:24:39.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你逃跑了\N{\rOriginal text}You ran.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.93,1:24:42.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是你最擅長的事\N{\rOriginal text}That's what you do best.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.35,1:24:46.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你這個備用版本的登月是個錯誤 我原本就不該參與\N{\rOriginal text}Your alternate version is wrong. I never should've been a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.10,1:24:47.23,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不幹了\N{\rOriginal text}I quit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.98,1:24:48.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}坐\N{\rOriginal text}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.70,1:24:59.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}今天你要扮演誰呢?\N{\rOriginal text}So, who are we gonna be today?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.66,1:25:01.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我來看看\N{\rOriginal text}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.74,1:25:03.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(目的地 希思羅機場)
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.08,1:25:06.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}海倫·帕克\N{\rOriginal text}Ooh, Helen Parker.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.91,1:25:09.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我打賭 你的英國口音一定很純正\N{\rOriginal text}I bet you do a killer British accent.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.25,1:25:13.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你想一走了之 去當海倫? 請便\N{\rOriginal text}You wanna take off and be Helen? Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.63,1:25:18.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}海倫不必提心吊膽地生活\N{\rOriginal text}Helen doesn't have to look over her shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.01,1:25:20.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}沒有人會來找你的\N{\rOriginal text}No one is coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.30,1:25:23.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除非呢?\N{\rOriginal text}Unless?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.30,1:25:28.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}除非你向任何人透露 阿爾忒彌斯計劃真實存在\N{\rOriginal text}Unless you ever tell anyone that Project Artemis was real,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.14,1:25:31.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月是虛假拍攝的\N{\rOriginal text}and the moon landing was fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.06,1:25:34.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}說到這個 計劃有變\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, on that score, change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.24,1:25:39.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們會播出備用版本的登月\N{\rOriginal text}we're going to air the alternate version.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.61,1:25:40.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}無論如何都播\N{\rOriginal text}No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.74,1:25:42.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們從來沒打算播出真實的登月\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, you were never gonna broadcast the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.91,1:25:44.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這不光是登月競賽\N{\rOriginal text}This isn't just a race for the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.91,1:25:50.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而是哪一種意識形態說了算的競賽\N{\rOriginal text}It is a race for which ideology gets to run things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.92,1:25:55.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我讓一個手下改裝了登月艙攝像機 讓它只傳回聲音\N{\rOriginal text}I got one of my men to rig the LEM camera so that it just beams back audio.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.38,1:26:00.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們會把他們的聲音同步到你的假舞台上\N{\rOriginal text}We're gonna sync with their sound and, uh, use your fake stage broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.68,1:26:02.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}從頭到尾播出\N{\rOriginal text}start to finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.09,1:26:07.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讓我第一個代表美國感謝你\N{\rOriginal text}Let me be the first to thank you on behalf of America.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.23,1:26:15.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 別難過 人人都能得到想要的結果\N{\rOriginal text}Come on, don't feel bad. Everybody gets what they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.23,1:26:19.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你可以展開新生活 不必再逃避過往\N{\rOriginal text}You get a new life with no past to run from.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.78,1:26:25.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}全世界也不必在共產主義的月光下入眠\N{\rOriginal text}And the world doesn't have to sleep under a communist moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.49,1:26:30.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 巴拿馬在召喚\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Panama beckons.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.71,1:26:35.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你最好快點 要趕不上飛機了 海倫\N{\rOriginal text}You better hurry. You're going to... miss your flight, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.13,1:26:42.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是為阿波羅號太空飛船上宇航員\N{\rOriginal text}This is a typical meal served to astronauts
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.26,1:26:44.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}提供的典型餐點\N{\rOriginal text}aboard Apollo space flights.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.14,1:26:46.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}燕麥片 吐司\N{\rOriginal text}Oatmeal, toast,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.47,1:26:51.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}和一個特製的零重力飲品袋 裝的是能量早餐飲品「果珍」\N{\rOriginal text}and a special zero-gravity pouch. Tang, the energy breakfast drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.27,1:26:53.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}其維生素C含量超過橙汁\N{\rOriginal text}And more vitamin C than orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.31,1:26:58.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能量果珍 太空人和地球家庭的選擇\N{\rOriginal text}Energy Tang, for spacemen and Earth families.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.27,1:27:02.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哥倫比亞廣播公司呈獻 《月球上的人》\N{\rOriginal text}CBS News presents Man On the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.91,1:27:06.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}講述阿波羅11號的史詩之旅\N{\rOriginal text}The epic journey of Apollo 11
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.16,1:27:09.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就在這歷史性事件的前夕\N{\rOriginal text}on the eve of that historic event.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.08,1:27:12.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}本節目由西部電氣贊助\N{\rOriginal text}Sponsored by Western Electric,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.71,1:27:15.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}西部電氣 貝爾系統的製造和供應單位\N{\rOriginal text}manufacturing and supply unit of the Bell System.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.71,1:27:19.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}本節目由國際紙業贊助 好主意在這裏繼續...\N{\rOriginal text}And by the International Paper Company, where good ideas roll on...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.30,1:27:25.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(阿波羅計劃中的人們)
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.78,1:28:31.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(假日酒店 祝阿波羅11號馬到成功)
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.87,1:28:36.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(私人活動 宇航員妻子的早午餐會)
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.72,1:28:49.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你怎麼來了?\N{\rOriginal text}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.31,1:28:54.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我得給你看一樣東西\N{\rOriginal text}I need to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.31,1:28:59.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這本來是個應急計劃\N{\rOriginal text}It was supposed to be a contingency plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.77,1:29:02.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他是這樣說服我的 就是個保險措施\N{\rOriginal text}That's how he sold it. It was an insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.27,1:29:03.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}以防我們失敗\N{\rOriginal text}In case we failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.07,1:29:07.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}知道了也好\N{\rOriginal text}It's good to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.70,1:29:09.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你從來沒相信過我們\N{\rOriginal text}that you never believed in us.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.91,1:29:10.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道你很難過\N{\rOriginal text}I know you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.99,1:29:12.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我理解 你理解什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}I understand... Oh, what do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.74,1:29:14.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請告訴我你理解什麼\N{\rOriginal text}Please tell me what you understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.74,1:29:16.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為你對真相一點都不理解\N{\rOriginal text}'Cause you don't understand shit about truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.62,1:29:18.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果你偽造這次任務...\N{\rOriginal text}If you fake this mission... If you fake this mission,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.67,1:29:22.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我們之前做出的每一次犧牲全都白費了\N{\rOriginal text}every single thing that we have sacrificed will have been for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.17,1:29:25.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我知道我搞砸了 我知道\N{\rOriginal text}I know I messed up. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.55,1:29:28.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你心裏清楚 如果沒有我 你們根本走不到今天\N{\rOriginal text}But you know you couldn't have made it to this day without me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.84,1:29:31.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我昨晚大可一走了之 但我沒有\N{\rOriginal text}I could've walked away last night, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.34,1:29:35.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我回來是為了彌補這個錯誤\N{\rOriginal text}I came back to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.18,1:29:38.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}彌補什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}Fix what?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.39,1:29:41.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫切斷了登月艙的畫面 如果我們不一起修好它\N{\rOriginal text}Moe cut the LEM camera, and if we don't fix this together
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.94,1:29:44.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那全世界看到的將會是這個版本\N{\rOriginal text}then this is gonna be the version that the world sees.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.82,1:29:50.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這不是應急計劃\N{\rOriginal text}It's not a contingency.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.95,1:29:56.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 你總能讓我別無選擇\N{\rOriginal text}God, you're so good at leaving me no options.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.54,1:30:03.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 我們去修好它\N{\rOriginal text}Fine, let's fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.88,1:30:07.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但等這事結束 我再也不想看到你\N{\rOriginal text}But when this is over, I never wanna see your face again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.77,1:30:24.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}為理查德·尼克松做事就是這種下場\N{\rOriginal text}This is what happens when you work for Richard Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.65,1:30:28.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我看了你的素描本 露比\N{\rOriginal text}I got your book, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.53,1:30:30.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你提早拆開了\N{\rOriginal text}You opened it early.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.32,1:30:32.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拆得正是時候\N{\rOriginal text}It came at just the right time.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.25,1:30:43.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}適合發射的大氣層\N{\rOriginal text}Proper atmosphere for launch
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.50,1:30:47.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是氧氣和氮氣的混合物\N{\rOriginal text}which is a combination of oxygen and nitrogen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.09,1:30:50.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}60%的氧氣和40%氮氣的大氣層\N{\rOriginal text}Sixty percent oxygen and 40% nitrogen atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.92,1:30:53.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}當然 宇航員們呼吸的是\N{\rOriginal text}Of course, the astronauts themselves are breathing pure oxygen
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.80,1:30:55.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太空服提供的純氧\N{\rOriginal text}through their space suits.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.14,1:30:59.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很快將進行另一次關鍵測試\N{\rOriginal text}Coming up shortly will be another key test
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.35,1:31:02.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}屆時發射組...\N{\rOriginal text}in which both the, uh, launch crew for the...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.06,1:31:04.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射載具組員和飛船乘組\N{\rOriginal text}the launch vehicle crew and the spacecraft team,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.69,1:31:08.52,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}會和指揮官尼爾·阿姆斯特朗一起\N{\rOriginal text}uh, combine together with the commander, Neil Armstrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.52,1:31:11.36,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}徹查緊急情況檢測系統\N{\rOriginal text}to make a thorough check of the Emergency Detection System.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.36,1:31:12.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這就是該系統...\N{\rOriginal text}This is the system...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.49,1:31:15.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們正在卡納維拉爾角直播 這創造歷史的一天天氣晴好\N{\rOriginal text}We're live from the Cape, where it's a beautiful day to make history.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.32,1:31:17.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們將在這裏為大家直播發射的部分\N{\rOriginal text}We'll be handling the launch portion of the broadcast from here,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.83,1:31:19.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們在休斯敦的同行\N{\rOriginal text}and our counterparts in Houston
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.45,1:31:21.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}將報道任務控制中心引導的\N{\rOriginal text}will be covering Apollo 11's historic flight,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.75,1:31:23.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅11號歷史性的航程\N{\rOriginal text}guided by Mission Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.55,1:31:31.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}各位\N{\rOriginal text}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.59,1:31:33.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}壞了\N{\rOriginal text}It's busted.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.93,1:31:35.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}攝像機的視頻前置放大器\N{\rOriginal text}The camera's video preamplifier.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.34,1:31:36.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}壞掉了 好吧 你能修好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}It's destroyed. Okay, can you fix that?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.89,1:31:38.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我也許能從電視上拆一個改裝 但...\N{\rOriginal text}I could maybe repurpose a part from a TV, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.72,1:31:40.64,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好啊 這裏有很多電視\N{\rOriginal text}Well, that's fine. There's plenty of TVs around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.64,1:31:42.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}航天局的電視都太老舊了\N{\rOriginal text}NASA's TVs... They are all too old.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.23,1:31:44.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要一台全新的晶體管彩色電視\N{\rOriginal text}I mean a brand-new solid-state color TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.94,1:31:46.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你多快能弄到一台?\N{\rOriginal text}Well, how fast can you get one?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.06,1:31:48.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你送我去電器商店最快要多久?\N{\rOriginal text}How fast can you get me to an electronics store?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.69,1:31:50.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我? 現在佛羅里達交通空前擁堵\N{\rOriginal text}Me? In the worst traffic in Florida history.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.69,1:31:51.94,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}走不開 得給大家做準備\N{\rOriginal text}I can't. I have to prep the guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.94,1:31:53.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}把鑰匙給我\N{\rOriginal text}Give me the keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.78,1:31:55.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好吧 我來拖延\N{\rOriginal text}Fine, I'll stall.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.95,1:31:57.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}快點 去吧...\N{\rOriginal text}Hurry. Go, go, go, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.62,1:32:05.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有酒店全部爆滿\N{\rOriginal text}Hotels are at capacity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.16,1:32:07.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}肯尼迪航天中心人滿為患\N{\rOriginal text}Kennedy Space Center is so crowded,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.21,1:32:09.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們聽說進出幾乎不可能\N{\rOriginal text}we're hearing it's nearly impossible to get in or out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.38,1:32:15.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉 開慢點\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.80,1:32:17.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}後面兩位還好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Are you guys good back there?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.09,1:32:18.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}很好 不好\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.60,1:32:22.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請別這樣...\N{\rOriginal text}Please, please stop. Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.60,1:32:28.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}到了 就是這家店\N{\rOriginal text}There it is. There's the store.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.87,1:32:44.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不 關門了\N{\rOriginal text}No! They're closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.21,1:32:47.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}關門了 什麼?\N{\rOriginal text}They're closed. Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.67,1:32:49.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 沒關門\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. No, they are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.04,1:32:51.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly. Whoa, whoa, whoa. Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.21,1:32:53.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們還等什麼呢? 快去\N{\rOriginal text}What are you waiting for? Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.55,1:32:55.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是... 好\N{\rOriginal text}Oh. Yeah, yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.09,1:32:57.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.18,1:33:00.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.26,1:33:01.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 這一台 很好 對 好\N{\rOriginal text}Yes, this one. This is great. Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.85,1:33:04.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很想幫忙 只是我不夠高 來吧 唐 好\N{\rOriginal text}I would help. I'm just not tall enough. Come on, Don. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.31,1:33:08.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 慢點 好的 各位 快點\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Slowly, all right. Guys, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.40,1:33:12.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天啊 我可不能蹲監獄\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, my God. I can't go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.94,1:33:14.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}交給我\N{\rOriginal text}Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.94,1:33:14.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(警察)
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.66,1:33:28.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她真厲害\N{\rOriginal text}She's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.58,1:33:30.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是啊\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.71,1:34:16.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一路順風 兄弟們\N{\rOriginal text}Have a good ride, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.22,1:34:23.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大約五分鐘後\N{\rOriginal text}In a matter of, uh, five minutes or so
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.55,1:34:26.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們將看到飛船指揮官尼爾·阿姆斯特朗\N{\rOriginal text}we'll be ready for the spacecraft commander, Neil Armstrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.43,1:34:29.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}跨過位於98米高空的舷門門檻\N{\rOriginal text}to come across the sill at the 320-foot level.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.49,1:34:47.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}搭乘穿梭麵包車... 快啊\N{\rOriginal text}The trip in the transfer van... Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.37,1:34:50.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大約要15分鐘才能抵達發射平台\N{\rOriginal text}Could take some 15 minutes or so to reach the pad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.33,1:34:54.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}屆時 宇航員將搭乘 兩部電梯中先來的那部\N{\rOriginal text}At which time the astronauts will board, uh, the first of two elevators
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.46,1:34:58.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}前往發射平台所在的98米高空\N{\rOriginal text}for the trip to the 320-foot level at the launchpad,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.80,1:35:02.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}然後進入飛船\N{\rOriginal text}uh, where they will then proceed to ingress the spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.51,1:35:07.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}站住 已經準備就緒了 小伙子\N{\rOriginal text}Whoa. We are locked and loaded, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.97,1:35:09.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不... 飛行部要把這個放進飛船\N{\rOriginal text}No, no. Flight Deck wants this on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.44,1:35:15.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏飛行部 放他過去 好\N{\rOriginal text}This is Flight Deck. Let him through. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.44,1:35:16.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}去吧\N{\rOriginal text}Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.48,1:35:21.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 我們必須啟動發射前的程序了 否則會錯過窗口期\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, we need to initiate prelaunch, or we lose the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.99,1:35:23.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}給他一分鐘就好\N{\rOriginal text}Just give him one minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.03,1:35:24.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}... 98米的高空\N{\rOriginal text}320-foot level,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.61,1:35:27.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}三位宇航員都已登上飛船\N{\rOriginal text}all three astronauts now aboard the spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.45,1:35:30.87,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幾分鐘前 宇航員巴茲·奧爾德林 進來坐在了中間的位置\N{\rOriginal text}A few minutes ago, Astronaut Buzz Aldrin, uh, came in and took the center seat...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.87,1:35:35.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我聽說船艙已經封閉 倒計時開始了\N{\rOriginal text}I'm hearing the cabin's now being sealed. Countdown has begun.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.46,1:35:38.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是他們發射時的姿態\N{\rOriginal text}These are the positions they will fly at liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.21,1:35:41.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}指揮官 這裏是飛船測試員 聽得清楚嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}CDR, STC, how do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.21,1:35:43.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飛船測試員 聽得很清楚\N{\rOriginal text}STC, loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.09,1:35:45.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}早上好 尼爾 發射架已撤開\N{\rOriginal text}Good morning, Neil. Gantry is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.34,1:35:46.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}歡迎登船\N{\rOriginal text}Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.51,1:35:49.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅11號準備發射 倒計時十分鐘\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11 is a go for launch in T-minus ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.60,1:35:51.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.81,1:35:56.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他回來了\N{\rOriginal text}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.90,1:35:58.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}接上了\N{\rOriginal text}It's connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.98,1:36:01.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}至少我認為接上了\N{\rOriginal text}At least I think I connected it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.82,1:36:04.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}斯圖 什麼意思?\N{\rOriginal text}Stu, what the hell does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.86,1:36:07.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我只有幾秒鐘時間 沒來得及進行壓力測試 我...\N{\rOriginal text}I only had a few seconds. I didn't have time to stress test it. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.25,1:36:13.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 坐下吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.67,1:36:18.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 都聽著\N{\rOriginal text}All right, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.97,1:36:26.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}無論今天這裏發生什麼\N{\rOriginal text}Whatever happens here today,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.43,1:36:29.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我都會支持你們做出的每一個決定\N{\rOriginal text}I will stand by every decision that you make.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.64,1:36:34.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}近十年來 超過四十萬人參與了這項計劃\N{\rOriginal text}Over 400,000 people have worked on this program for nearly ten years.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.02,1:36:36.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就為了實現一個人對全世界的承諾\N{\rOriginal text}All to keep one man's promise to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.73,1:36:38.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讓我們堅守這個承諾吧\N{\rOriginal text}So, let's keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.07,1:36:44.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好了 告訴我發射是否就緒吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Give me, "Go/No go" for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.40,1:36:47.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}收到 所有崗位 準備進行最後的就緒核查\N{\rOriginal text}Ah, roger. All stations, stand by for final "Go/No go."
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.16,1:36:48.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}機械姿態電控 就緒\N{\rOriginal text}MACE. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.24,1:36:49.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}環境控制系統 就緒\N{\rOriginal text}ECS. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.62,1:36:51.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}電力系統 就緒\N{\rOriginal text}EPS. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.16,1:36:52.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}序列控制器 就緒\N{\rOriginal text}Sequencer. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.41,1:36:53.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}導航系統 就緒\N{\rOriginal text}GNS. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.66,1:36:56.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}航天器控制系統 這裏最精彩了\N{\rOriginal text}SCS. This is the best part.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.29,1:36:59.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他們依次問下去 每一個...\N{\rOriginal text}They go down the line and every single...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.04,1:37:02.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}每一個技術員都必須說 發射「就緒」或「未就緒」\N{\rOriginal text}every single technician has to say, "Go," or, "No go," for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.17,1:37:03.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}任何一人都能阻止發射\N{\rOriginal text}Any one of them can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.84,1:37:07.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}CFAT CSE 現在能回答「就緒」了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}CFAT. CSE, can you give me a "go" now?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.05,1:37:08.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}CSE就緒\N{\rOriginal text}CSE is go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.13,1:37:10.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 鷹號就緒\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. Uh, Eagle is go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.78,1:37:27.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}CBTS 這裏是CSA9號\N{\rOriginal text}CBTS, this is CSA 9.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.78,1:37:29.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}倒計時20秒\N{\rOriginal text}Twenty seconds and counting.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.20,1:37:34.08,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}倒計時15秒 制導系統已切換為自主模式\N{\rOriginal text}T-minus 15 seconds. Guidance is internal.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.70,1:37:39.42,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}十二 十一 十 九...\N{\rOriginal text}Twelve, eleven, ten, nine...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.46,1:37:43.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}點火程序啟動\N{\rOriginal text}Ignition sequence starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.35,1:38:00.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}五 四 三 二 一\N{\rOriginal text}Five, four, three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.10,1:38:01.60,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}所有引擎啟動\N{\rOriginal text}All engines running.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.26,1:38:32.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射 火箭升空\N{\rOriginal text}Liftoff. We have liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.31,1:38:41.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}發射塔已分離\N{\rOriginal text}Tower clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.35,1:38:45.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}休斯敦 交給你了\N{\rOriginal text}Houston, she's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.64,1:39:59.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫·伯克斯來了 要找你們倆\N{\rOriginal text}Moe Berkus is here. For both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.60,1:40:02.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅11號已經升空\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11 is on the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.48,1:40:04.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}四十萬公里之外\N{\rOriginal text}250,000 miles away,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.56,1:40:08.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}月球在等待人類的首次到來\N{\rOriginal text}where the moon is waiting for man's first arrival.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.86,1:40:11.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}整個航程要用三天時間\N{\rOriginal text}Flight to take, uh, three days.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.07,1:40:14.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}飛船要抵達...\N{\rOriginal text}And, uh, the, uh, spacecraft to reach there...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.53,1:40:16.07,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉全都告訴我了\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.78,1:40:21.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好極了\N{\rOriginal text}Bravissimo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.37,1:40:23.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}省省吧 這是創造歷史\N{\rOriginal text}Shove it. That was history.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.12,1:40:25.37,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嗨 海倫 抱歉 是凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Hi, Helen. Uh, sorry, Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.37,1:40:28.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我聽說你回來了 所以我也回來了\N{\rOriginal text}I heard you came back, so I came back too.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.67,1:40:34.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 去月球片場看了一眼\N{\rOriginal text}I... I took a little peeky-poo at the moon set,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.72,1:40:37.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}真是完美\N{\rOriginal text}and it is perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.01,1:40:39.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幹得好\N{\rOriginal text}Great job.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.01,1:40:42.22,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}如果你認為我會讓你播出 這次任務的造假版本\N{\rOriginal text}If you think that I'm gonna let you broadcast some fake version of this,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.22,1:40:43.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那我現在就去找媒體\N{\rOriginal text}I'll go to the press right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.73,1:40:45.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科爾\N{\rOriginal text}Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.44,1:40:48.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科爾...\N{\rOriginal text}Cole. Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.19,1:40:56.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你... 去找媒體吧 帶他們看看月球片場\N{\rOriginal text}You, uh... You go to the press. Bring 'em by the moon set,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.57,1:41:02.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但你要知道 今後再也不會有人相信國家航空航天局了\N{\rOriginal text}but just know that no one will ever trust the legitimacy of NASA again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.54,1:41:05.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是國家安全問題\N{\rOriginal text}This is a matter of national security.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.54,1:41:08.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}本次直播必須在可控的情況下進行\N{\rOriginal text}This broadcast must take place in a controlled setting.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.79,1:41:11.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你應該最明白了\N{\rOriginal text}You of all people must understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.21,1:41:15.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}任務的重點已經不再是登月了\N{\rOriginal text}The mission isn't about landing on the moon anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.97,1:41:21.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而是全世界在電視上觀看美國戰勝蘇聯\N{\rOriginal text}It is about the world watching America beat Russia on TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.85,1:41:29.27,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我得趕飛機\N{\rOriginal text}I got a flight to catch.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.65,1:41:36.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我會及時趕回來看登月直播的\N{\rOriginal text}I'll be back in time for the lunar broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.15,1:41:37.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我想在這裏看\N{\rOriginal text}I thought I'd watch it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.49,1:41:40.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉 和你一起在月球片場看\N{\rOriginal text}With you, Kelly. On the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.04,1:41:51.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 我們正在創造歷史\N{\rOriginal text}Hey. We're making history.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.33,1:42:26.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你說我的那些話全都沒錯\N{\rOriginal text}Everything you said about me is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.70,1:42:28.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我是個騙子 一直都是\N{\rOriginal text}I'm a con artist, and I always have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.87,1:42:33.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我的真名甚至不是凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}My real name is not even Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.84,1:42:38.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那些我跟你講的故事\N{\rOriginal text}All those stories that I told you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.38,1:42:40.67,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}說我和我媽挨家挨戶推銷\N{\rOriginal text}about my mom and I selling products door-to-door,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.68,1:42:41.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那是真事\N{\rOriginal text}those were true.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.97,1:42:44.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但都是騙局\N{\rOriginal text}They were all scams.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.39,1:42:47.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們開始只是小打小鬧 之後越做越大\N{\rOriginal text}And we started out small, and then they got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.43,1:42:51.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}大到涉及地產和保險什麼的\N{\rOriginal text}Like real estate and insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.35,1:42:52.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}然後...\N{\rOriginal text}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.44,1:42:58.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我16歲那年 在北達科他州 有個人掏槍了\N{\rOriginal text}when I was 16, a guy in North Dakota pulled a gun
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.86,1:43:01.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我媽比他更快掏出槍 把他打死了\N{\rOriginal text}and my mom pulled hers out first and she killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.86,1:43:04.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她叫我逃跑 我照做了\N{\rOriginal text}And she told me to run and I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.53,1:43:07.79,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}她進了監獄 我再也沒見過她\N{\rOriginal text}And she went to prison and I never saw her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.96,1:43:15.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我偽造文件 用假名來找工作\N{\rOriginal text}And I forged documents and used fake names to get jobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.38,1:43:19.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我去紐約後發現了廣告業\N{\rOriginal text}And when I went to New York, I found advertising.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.38,1:43:23.97,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}就像我媽教我的騙局 但卻合法\N{\rOriginal text}And that was like the scams that my mom taught me, but it was legal.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.39,1:43:29.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我騙了很多人\N{\rOriginal text}And I lied to so many people.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.35,1:43:32.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}最糟糕的謊言是我對自己說的那些\N{\rOriginal text}The worst lies were the ones I told myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.56,1:43:36.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}說所有人都在騙人 這只是一場大型遊戲而已\N{\rOriginal text}That everybody does it. You know. It's just a big game.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.52,1:43:40.15,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但後來我來了這裏\N{\rOriginal text}But then I came down here...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.45,1:43:44.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}認識了你\N{\rOriginal text}I met you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.24,1:43:52.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我瞭解到參與到真實事件中是什麼感受\N{\rOriginal text}I learned what it was like to be a part of something real.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.67,1:43:58.96,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫提出的條件是抹去我的黑歷史\N{\rOriginal text}Moe offered me a way to erase my past.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.96,1:44:00.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我原以為那就是我想要的 但...\N{\rOriginal text}I thought that's what I wanted, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.38,1:44:05.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不想再逃亡了\N{\rOriginal text}I don't wanna run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.02,1:44:16.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫是個值得尊敬的對手 但他遇到旗鼓相當的人了\N{\rOriginal text}Moe is a worthy opponent, but he has met his match.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.82,1:44:24.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我保證這是我最後一次 用欺騙的手段來獲取我想要的東西\N{\rOriginal text}I promise this is the last time I will trick anyone into getting what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.28,1:44:27.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我保證\N{\rOriginal text}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.74,1:44:31.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你覺得不撒謊也能做到嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you think you can do it without lying?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.62,1:44:35.62,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}絕對不行 好吧 我想也是\N{\rOriginal text}Absolutely not. Yeah, I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.25,1:44:42.38,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那你有什麼計劃?\N{\rOriginal text}So, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.30,1:44:46.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們為什麼在這裏碰頭?\N{\rOriginal text}Why are we meeting out here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.18,1:44:49.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為莫監聽一切對話 這人就像個魔術師 無處不在\N{\rOriginal text}Because Moe bugs everything. The guy's like Houdini. He's everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.80,1:44:52.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 莫不知道我們修好了登月艙攝像機\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, so, Moe doesn't know that we fixed the LEM camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.72,1:44:54.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們就此來制定計劃\N{\rOriginal text}We build a plan around that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.18,1:44:57.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們只需讓他相信我們在直播假登月\N{\rOriginal text}All we have to do is convince him that we are broadcasting the fake moon landing,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.90,1:45:00.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}而實際上我們在播真的\N{\rOriginal text}when in reality we're broadcasting the real one.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.69,1:45:02.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們有沒有辦法給設備動手腳\N{\rOriginal text}Is there a way that we could rig the equipment
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.73,1:45:05.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}來播出真實的登月艙視頻?\N{\rOriginal text}so that it actually sends out the real LEM video feed?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.24,1:45:07.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}拜託 兩位\N{\rOriginal text}Come on, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.24,1:45:09.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們連登月都搞定了 給我個假設理論啊\N{\rOriginal text}You figured out how to land on the moon. Give me a hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.70,1:45:13.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 假設的話 我們可以重新接線\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, um, hypothetically, we could rewire it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.58,1:45:16.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}讓設備只接收任務控制中心的播出信號\N{\rOriginal text}So that it only picks up the broadcast signal from Mission Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.25,1:45:18.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 然後和我們的信號同步 對\N{\rOriginal text}Sure, then sync it with our feed. Hmm. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.17,1:45:25.21,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}嘿 各位\N{\rOriginal text}Hey, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.05,1:45:28.63,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫·伯克斯派這兩位來測試播出信號\N{\rOriginal text}Moe Berkus sent these guys to test the broadcast feed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.64,1:45:31.30,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}莫... 伯克斯 對 莫·伯克斯...\N{\rOriginal text}Moe... Moe Berk... Yes. Moe Berk... Moe Berkus.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.39,1:45:34.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們誰都沒接到電話?\N{\rOriginal text}Telling me none of you got the phone call?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.10,1:45:37.06,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好極了 攝像機在哪?\N{\rOriginal text}Great. All right, where's the camera?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.23,1:45:42.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你還好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Are you okay? Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.44,1:45:44.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請你們快點好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you guys hurry up, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.94,1:45:47.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}唐 你把煙掐了吧\N{\rOriginal text}Don, maybe just take the cigarette out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.99,1:45:50.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抱歉... 我之前從沒吸過煙\N{\rOriginal text}I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I've just never smoked a cigarette before.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.12,1:45:53.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我不喜歡\N{\rOriginal text}I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.45,1:45:57.29,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}11號 這裏是休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, 11, this is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.29,1:45:58.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}環月軌道進入就緒 完畢\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, you are go for LOI. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.50,1:46:00.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}確認 向月球前進\N{\rOriginal text}Confirmed. On track for the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.25,1:46:02.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿波羅11號 這裏是休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Apollo 11, this is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.13,1:46:04.59,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你的全部系統正常 要轉到月球後面了\N{\rOriginal text}All your systems are looking good. Going around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.59,1:46:06.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們另一邊見 完畢\N{\rOriginal text}We'll see you on the other side. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.13,1:46:08.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們失去了信號\N{\rOriginal text}And we've had loss of signal
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.05,1:46:10.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}因為阿波羅11號飛到了月球後面\N{\rOriginal text}as Apollo 11 goes behind the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.18,1:46:14.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}現在是東部夏令時下午3點半\N{\rOriginal text}It's now 3:30 Eastern Daylight Time.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.51,1:46:18.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}3點46分時 我們應該能夠收到 登月艙的第一個信號\N{\rOriginal text}At 3:46 we should be getting the first signal from the Lunar Module.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.69,1:46:21.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}估計觀眾有上億人\N{\rOriginal text}The estimated audience: hundreds of millions.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.31,1:46:23.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}可能有四億人\N{\rOriginal text}Perhaps 400 million persons or so are watching
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.98,1:46:27.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}正在觀看這一重大事件的直播...\N{\rOriginal text}this broadcast today of, uh, the greatest event...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.82,1:46:28.90,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}兄弟們\N{\rOriginal text}Boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.36,1:46:31.74,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 開始吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.79,1:46:42.58,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}再往下一點 很好 各位\N{\rOriginal text}A little bit more. Well done, guys.
