Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.92,1:53:06.55,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我就知道我找對人了\N{\rOriginal text}I knew I hired the right people.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.93,1:53:09.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 來吧\N{\rOriginal text}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.01,1:53:12.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}(真實信號 播出信號)
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.81,1:53:14.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}天衣無縫 真難以置信\N{\rOriginal text}It's seamless. It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.02,1:53:18.10,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我來到舷梯底部了\N{\rOriginal text}I'm at the foot of the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.60,1:53:22.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}登月艙的支腳僅僅壓進月球表面2到5厘米\N{\rOriginal text}The LEM footpads are only depressed in the surface about one or two inches,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.98,1:53:28.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不過靠近了看 月表的塵土似乎非常細膩\N{\rOriginal text}although the surface appears to be very, very fine-grained as you get close to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.61,1:53:33.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}幾乎就像粉末 下面的塵埃非常細\N{\rOriginal text}It's almost like a powder. Down there, it's very fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.50,1:53:36.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我要走下登月艙了\N{\rOriginal text}I'm gonna step off the LEM now.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.21,1:53:44.80,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是個人的一小步\N{\rOriginal text}That's one small step for man...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.30,1:53:51.72,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}卻是人類的一大步\N{\rOriginal text}one giant leap for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.14,1:53:59.54,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這麼精彩的話 我們可能得花好幾年才想得出\N{\rOriginal text}We could have spent years coming up with something that good.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.69,1:54:02.19,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是的\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.90,1:54:05.57,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是劇本裏的嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Was that, uh, in the script?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.57,1:54:07.03,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不是\N{\rOriginal text}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.36,1:54:09.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這句台詞不錯\N{\rOriginal text}That's a good line.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.54,1:54:17.91,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}一級一級舷梯跳下來是很簡單的\N{\rOriginal text}It's a very simple matter to hop down from one step to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.41,1:54:20.25,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾要展示牌匾了\N{\rOriginal text}Neil is now unveiling the plaque.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.38,1:54:23.34,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}「地球的人類\N{\rOriginal text}"Here man, from the planet Earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.34,1:54:28.47,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}於公元1969年7月首次踏上月球\N{\rOriginal text}first set foot upon the moon, July 1969 AD.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.47,1:54:31.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們為全人類的和平而來」\N{\rOriginal text}We came in peace for all mankind."
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.06,1:54:35.89,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}準備好上鏡了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You ready for the camera?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.89,1:54:39.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾 這裏是休斯敦 視野正常\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, Neil, this is Houston. The field of view is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.31,1:54:42.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們希望你把攝像機對準右邊一點 完畢\N{\rOriginal text}We'd like you to aim it a little bit more to the right. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.52,1:54:43.61,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好\N{\rOriginal text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.57,1:54:46.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太往右了\N{\rOriginal text}Too much to the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.11,1:54:48.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能往左4 5度嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Can you bring it back left about, uh, four or five degrees?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.62,1:54:55.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 看起來不錯 尼爾\N{\rOriginal text}Okay. That looks good, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.91,1:54:59.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}哥倫比亞號... 這裏是休斯敦 接收信號 完畢\N{\rOriginal text}Columbia, Columbia, this is Houston, AOS. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.41,1:55:01.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾阿姆斯特朗目前已經在月球表面\N{\rOriginal text}Neil Armstrong has been on the lunar surface now
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.92,1:55:03.04,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}停留近45分鐘了\N{\rOriginal text}almost 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.58,1:55:06.00,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}寧靜海基地 這裏是休斯敦\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, Tranquility Base, this is Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.00,1:55:08.46,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}請兩位一起走進鏡頭一下好嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Could we get both of you on the camera for a minute, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.22,1:55:13.26,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}美國總統想跟你們說幾句 完畢\N{\rOriginal text}The President of the United States would like to say a few words to you. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.26,1:55:15.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是我們的榮幸\N{\rOriginal text}That would be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.68,1:55:17.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好 總統先生 請講吧\N{\rOriginal text}All right, go ahead, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.68,1:55:18.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這裏是休斯敦 完畢\N{\rOriginal text}This is Houston. Out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.77,1:55:20.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們好 尼爾和巴茲\N{\rOriginal text}Hello, Neil and Buzz.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.27,1:55:25.56,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我正在白宮的橢圓辦公室 用電話跟你們通話\N{\rOriginal text}I am talking to you by telephone from the Oval Room at the White House...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.57,1:55:27.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這地方到處都是特勤局的人\N{\rOriginal text}They have Secret Service all over this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.73,1:55:31.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這絕對是有史以來最重要的一次通話\N{\rOriginal text}And this certainly has to be the most historic telephone call ever made.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.32,1:55:34.95,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你們跟我們通話的同時...\N{\rOriginal text}And as you talk to us...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.95,1:55:37.45,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我覺得你跟他真的很像\N{\rOriginal text}He actually reminds me a lot of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.45,1:55:40.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}別這麼說 真的 連玩笑都別開\N{\rOriginal text}Do not say that. No, don't even joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.71,1:55:45.13,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}總統發表無聊講話時我們要待命 別動\N{\rOriginal text}We're still holding while the president drones on. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.13,1:55:46.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}阿姆斯特朗 我主要盯著你\N{\rOriginal text}Armstrong, I'm watching you the most.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.84,1:55:51.17,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}在這全人類史上無比珍貴的時刻...\N{\rOriginal text}For one priceless moment in the whole history of man...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.17,1:55:52.76,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}肯尼迪航天中心 我們直接通話吧\N{\rOriginal text}Kennedy, let's go direct.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.22,1:55:57.39,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}科爾 你收到畫面了嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Cole, are you receiving picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.39,1:55:59.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這邊的視頻信號燈沒亮\N{\rOriginal text}The video feed light isn't on up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.18,1:56:02.35,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾 什麼意思? 壞掉了?\N{\rOriginal text}Uh, what do you mean, Neil? It's not working?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.35,1:56:04.40,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}那得你來告訴我 你能看到畫面嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}You tell me. Do you see picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.90,1:56:07.31,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們的攝像機發出了電力過載警報\N{\rOriginal text}We're getting a power surge warning on the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.32,1:56:09.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}好像壞了 你還能看到我們嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}I think it crapped out. Can you still see us?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.78,1:56:11.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}能 還能看見\N{\rOriginal text}Yeah, I can still see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.61,1:56:14.78,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}稍等 尼爾\N{\rOriginal text}Um, one second, Neil.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.28,1:56:17.16,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}尼爾說月球上的視頻信號燈沒有亮\N{\rOriginal text}Neil's saying the video feed light isn't on up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.16,1:56:18.49,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你確定那台攝像機能用?\N{\rOriginal text}Are you sure that camera's working?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.49,1:56:20.70,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我安裝了新零件 應該沒問題的 但...\N{\rOriginal text}I installed the new part. It should be working just fine but...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.70,1:56:23.12,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}但什麼? 但我... 當時趕時間\N{\rOriginal text}But what? But I... I was in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.62,1:56:25.71,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}見鬼\N{\rOriginal text}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.50,1:56:30.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}怎麼了?\N{\rOriginal text}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.51,1:56:33.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們不確定登月艙上的 攝像機是否運作正常\N{\rOriginal text}We're not sure that the camera on the LEM is working.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.88,1:56:36.51,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我覺得播出的畫面是你們的\N{\rOriginal text}I think that's your feed broadcasting.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.22,1:56:40.14,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}電視上的畫面和片場一樣嗎?\N{\rOriginal text}Does the feed on your TV look like your set?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.93,1:56:44.81,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我... 看不出是不是我們\N{\rOriginal text}I... I can't tell if it's us.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.81,1:56:47.98,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}測試一下 讓一個特工揮揮手什麼的\N{\rOriginal text}Test it. Have one of your agents give a little wave or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.52,1:56:51.44,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不行 所有人都在這裏\N{\rOriginal text}I can't. Everyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.63,1:57:10.75,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這是什麼鬼? 我不知道\N{\rOriginal text}What the hell is that? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.38,1:57:14.01,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}他差5厘米就進鏡頭了\N{\rOriginal text}He is two inches away from being on that screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.01,1:57:15.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是... 2厘米\N{\rOriginal text}It's... It's one inch.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.09,1:57:16.84,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}這也是你那該死的劇本裏的情節?\N{\rOriginal text}Is that in your goddamn script?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.18,1:57:20.68,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}約瑟夫 有新加的戲?\N{\rOriginal text}Joseph, were there new pages?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.68,1:57:23.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不僅代表美國\N{\rOriginal text}Representing not only the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.43,1:57:25.69,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}也代表所有國家熱愛和平的人\N{\rOriginal text}but men of peace of all nations...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.94,1:57:32.65,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}是小淘氣 天啊 貓咪...\N{\rOriginal text}Oh, Mischief! Oh, God. Kitty, kitty! Pss, kitty, kitty, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.65,1:57:33.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}小淘氣...\N{\rOriginal text}Mischief! Mischief!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.86,1:57:35.32,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你去哪?\N{\rOriginal text}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.28,1:57:37.86,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}小淘氣... 凱莉\N{\rOriginal text}Mischief. Mischief. K... Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.86,1:57:39.41,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}過來 那隻貓?\N{\rOriginal text}Come here. The cat?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.41,1:57:40.83,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}過來...\N{\rOriginal text}Come here. Come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.33,1:57:51.09,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}你認識這隻貓?\N{\rOriginal text}Do you know this cat?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.92,1:57:54.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}貓咪...\N{\rOriginal text}Kitty, kitty, kitty!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.05,1:57:56.88,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}過來 小寶... 過來 你個小混蛋\N{\rOriginal text}Come here, you sweet... Come here, you little bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.88,1:57:58.43,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}貓咪...\N{\rOriginal text}Kitty, kitty, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.43,1:58:00.05,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}給我過來 不\N{\rOriginal text}Come here, you! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.26,1:58:05.18,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉 你那邊到底怎麼了?\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly, what the hell is going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.18,1:58:06.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}凱莉?\N{\rOriginal text}Kelly? Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.48,1:58:09.02,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}繞到後面去\N{\rOriginal text}Go round the back!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.02,1:58:10.73,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}小淘氣...\N{\rOriginal text}Mischief! Mischief!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.07,1:58:13.11,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}貓咪...\N{\rOriginal text}Kitty, kitty, kitty!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.11,1:58:15.28,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}抓住它... 快...\N{\rOriginal text}Catch him! Catch him! Oh! Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.28,1:58:16.53,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我們走 快\N{\rOriginal text}Let's go! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.11,1:58:20.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}來 沒事的\N{\rOriginal text}Come here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.99,1:58:22.82,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}小淘氣 過來吧\N{\rOriginal text}Mischief. Just come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.83,1:58:24.24,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}閉嘴...\N{\rOriginal text}Just shut up. Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.24,1:58:27.33,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}過來 貓咪... 過來 小寶寶 你認識我的\N{\rOriginal text}Come here, kitty, kitty, kitty. Come here, little baby. You know me.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.67,1:58:29.92,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}不\N{\rOriginal text}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.26,1:58:45.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}非常感謝\N{\rOriginal text}And thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.85,1:58:47.77,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我很期待 我們都很期待\N{\rOriginal text}and I look forward, all of us look forward,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.77,1:58:49.85,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}星期四在大黃蜂號上見到你們\N{\rOriginal text}to seeing you on the Hornet on Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.48,1:58:55.48,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}我也很期待 先生\N{\rOriginal text}I look forward to that very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.74,1:58:59.99,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}播出的是你的人 科爾\N{\rOriginal text}Those are your guys, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.53,1:59:02.66,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}太好了 是我們的人\N{\rOriginal text}Yes! Those are our guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.70,1:59:08.50,Translated text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微软雅黑 Light}對 我知道你們都知道\N{\rOriginal text}Yes. I know you know that.
